# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:13
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_99711a67:

    # "A light breeze causes the naked branches overhead to rattle like wooden windchimes."
    "Un ventet suau fa que les branques nues que hi ha enlaire sonin com si fossin campanetes de fusta."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:15
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_0ca9b69a:

    # "This is a popular retreat for couples in the summer. The deciduous trees provide a beautiful green canopy, far out of sight of teachers and fellow students."
    "Aquest és un lloc de retir popular a l'estiu per a parelles. Els arbres de fulla caduca ofereixen un preciós dosser verd, fora de la vista de professors i altres estudiants."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:17
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_808f86a6:

    # "But now, in late winter, it feels like I'm standing under a pile of kindling."
    "Però ara, a finals d'hivern, em sento com si estigués sota una pila de branquetes per fer foc."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:19
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_dff2025d:

    # "I breathe into my cupped hands and rub them together furiously to prevent them from numbing in this cold."
    "Per evitar que les mans se m'entumeixin del fred, els hi tiro l'alè i me les frego amb força."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:21
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_48c2e508:

    # hi "Just how long am I expected to wait out here, anyway? I'm sure the note said 4:00 PM."
    hi "Però, quant de temps se suposa que m'he d'esperar aquí? N'estic segur que a la nota hi deia a les quatre de la tarda."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:23
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_d39923ee:

    # "Ah yes… the note… slipped between the pages of my math book while I wasn't looking."
    "Ah, sí… la nota… que m'han deixat d'amagat entre les pàgines del llibre de matemàtiques."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:25
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_63f623d0:

    # "As far as clichés go, I'm more a fan of the letter-in-the-locker, but at least this way shows a bit of initiative."
    "Posats a fer servir clixés, soc més fan de la típica carta a la taquilla, però en tot cas aquesta manera mostra una mica més d'iniciativa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:27
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_e1a8950a:

    # "As I ponder the meaning of the note, the snowfall gradually thickens."
    "Em pregunto quin deu ser el significat de la nota, mentre cada cop neva més i més."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:29
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_7413796f:

    # "The snowflakes silently falling from the white-painted sky are the only sign of time passing in this stagnant world."
    "Els flocs de neu que cauen silenciosament del cel blanc són l'únic senyal qui es veu del pas del temps en un món que sembla haver-se aturat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:31
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_950e1e4b:

    # "Their slow descent upon the frozen forest makes it seem like time has slowed to a crawl."
    "El seu lent descens sobre el bosc congelat fa que sembli que el temps s'ha alentit."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:35
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_2eef6555:

    # "The rustling of dry snow underfoot startles me, interrupting the quiet mood. Someone is approaching me from behind."
    "El so de cruixent de trepitjades a la neu seca em sobresalta i altera la tranquil·litat. Algú se m'està apropant des de darrere."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:37
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_520d792a:

    # mystery "Hi… Hisao? You came?"
    mystery "Hi… Hisao? Has vingut?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:39
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_d8f7b97d:

    # "A hesitating, barely audible question."
    "Una pregunta indecisa i quasi inaudible."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:41
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_e9d15ede:

    # "However, I recognize the owner of that dainty voice instantly."
    "Amb tot, reconec la propietària d'aquesta veu delicada a l'instant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:43
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_ee887742:

    # "I feel my heart skip a beat."
    "Noto el cor em fa un salt."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:45
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_58c40c96:

    # "It's a voice I've listened to hundreds of times, but never as more than an eavesdropper to a conversation."
    "És una veu que he sentit centenars de vegades, tot i que mai més enllà d'escoltar-lo com un intrús."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:47
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_7b25dee1:

    # "I turn to face this voice, the voice of my dreams, and my heart begins to race…"
    "Em giro per mirar qui fa aquesta veu, la veu dels meus somnis, i el cor se m'accelera…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:53
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_4a5ac0e4:

    # hi "Iwanako? I got a note telling me to wait here… it was yours?"
    hi "Iwanako? M'he trobat una nota dient-me que vingué aquí… era teva?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:55
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_10578e26:

    # "Dammit. I spent all afternoon trying to come up with a good line and that was the result."
    "Collons. M'he passat tota la tarda intentant pensar en una bona frase i aquest ha estat el resultat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:57
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_04cf4a2b:

    # "Pathetic."
    "Patètic."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:59
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_dc34d5c5:

    # "Iwanako" "Ahmm… yes. I asked a friend to give you that note… I'm so glad you got it."
    "Iwanako" "Ahmm… sí. Li he demanat a una amiga que et donés la nota… m'alegra tant que t'hagi arribat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:61
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_9865b953:

    # "A shy, joyous smile that makes me so tense I couldn't move a single muscle even if I tried."
    "Fa un somriure tímid i alegre, que em posa tan tens que no podria moure ni un sol múscul encara que ho intentés."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:85
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_16882f25:

    # "My heart is pounding now, as if it were trying to burst out from my chest and claim this girl for itself."
    "El cor se'm desboca, talment com si em volgués sortir disparat del pit i reclamar aquesta noia per a ell mateix."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:91
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_b27fb624:

    # hi "So… ah… here we are. Out in the cold…"
    hi "Bé… ah… doncs aquí estem. Aquí fora, amb el fred…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:93
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_2aedc789:

    # "Once again, the wind stirs up the branches. The cacophonous noise is music to my ears."
    "Una altra vegada, el vent sacseja les branques. El so cacofònic és música per a les meves orelles."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:95
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_33f42f60:

    # "Iwanako flinches ever so softly against the gust of wind."
    "La Iwanako té una petita esgarrifança per les ràfegues de vent."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:97
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_b991226f:

    # "As it passes, she rights herself, as if supported by some new confidence."
    "Quan li passa, es redreça, com si l'animés una nova confiança."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:99
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_b4d17b0b:

    # "Her eyes lock with mine and she lazily twirls her long, dark hair around her finger."
    "Em clava els ulls mentre es recargola mandrosament la seva llarga i fosca cabellera al voltant del dit."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:101
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_15e570dd:

    # "All the while, the anxious beating of my heart grows louder."
    "Mentrestant, els angoixosos batecs del cor se'm fan més forts."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:107
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_592a62b5:

    # "My throat is tight; I doubt I could even force a word out if I tried."
    "Tinc un nus a la gola: per molt que ho intentés, dubto que ara pogués dir ni una sola paraula."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:109
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_ae21233d:

    # "Iwanako" "You see…"
    "Iwanako" "Veuràs…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:118
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_2021a2e6:

    # "Iwanako" "…I wanted to know…"
    "Iwanako" "…volia saber…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:138
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_1f544bbd:

    # "Iwanako" "… if you'd go out with me…"
    "Iwanako" "…si t'agradaria sortir amb mi…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:140
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_6c61e701:

    # "I stand there, motionless, save for my pounding heart."
    "M'estic allà plantat, immòbil, excepte pel batec del meu cor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:142
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_c6865dbb:

    # "I want to say something in reply, but my vocal cords feel like they've been stretched beyond the breaking point."
    "Vull respondre alguna cosa, però em sento com si les cordes vocals se m'haguessin tensat més enllà del límit."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:146
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_8c200948:

    # "Iwanako" "… Hisao?"
    "Iwanako" "…Hisao?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:148
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_2c1773f6:

    # "I reach up to try to massage my throat, but this only sends spikes of blinding pain along my arms."
    "Aixeco la mà per intentar fer-me fregues al coll, però això només em produeix unes punxades de dolor molt intenses als braços."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:150
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_5de9e5a4:

    # "Iwanako" "Hisao?!"
    "Iwanako" "Hisao?!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:159
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_b126c492:

    # "My whole body freezes, save for my eyes, which shoot open in terror."
    "Se'm congela tot el cos, tret dels ulls, que s'obren aterrits."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:195
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_c2d52363:

    # "Iwanako" "HISAO!"
    "Iwanako" "HISAO!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:197
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_1c8e79cf:

    # "The beating in my chest suddenly stops, and I go weak at the knees."
    "Els batecs del meu pit s'aturen tot d'una, i em tremolen els genolls."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:203
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_e91b5073:

    # n "{vspace=210}The world around me - the canopy of bare branches, the dull winter sky, Iwanako running towards me - all these fade to black."
    n "{vspace=210}El món que m'envolta - el dosser de branques nues, l'opac cel hivernal, la Iwanako corrent cap a mi - tot es torna negre."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:205
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_3fd9ad67:

    # n "{vspace=30}The last things I remember before slipping away are the sounds of Iwanako screaming for help and the incessant clatter of the branches above…"
    n "{vspace=30}L'últim que recordo abans de desmaiar-me del tot són els crits de la Iwanako demanant ajuda i l'incessant soroll de les branques a sobre meu…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:209
translate ca a1_monday_out_cold_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:222
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_84705307:

    # centered "It's been four months since my heart attack."
    centered "Han passat quatre mesos des del meu atac de cor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:235
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_64089ab5:

    # n "{vspace=60}In that whole time, I can probably count the times I've left this hospital room unsupervised on one hand."
    n "{vspace=60}En tot aquest temps, probablement puc comptar amb els dits d'una mà les vegades que he sortit d'aquesta habitació d'hospital sense supervisió."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:237
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_c0a05b40:

    # n "Four months is a pretty long time when you're left alone with your thoughts. So, I've had plenty of time to come to terms with my situation."
    n "Quatre mesos és molt de temps quan et quedes sol amb els teus pensaments. Per tant, he tingut prou temps per acceptar la meva situació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:239
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_0b1ec2a4:

    # n "Arrhythmia."
    n "Arrítmia."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:241
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_0e96e733:

    # n "A strange word. A foreign, alien one. One that you don't want to be in the same room with."
    n "Una paraula estranya. Desconeguda, aliena. Una amb la que no vols compartir habitació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:243
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_96ac1846:

    # n "A rare condition. It causes the heart to act erratically and occasionally beat way too fast. It can be fatal."
    n "Una malaltia poc freqüent. Fa que el cor actuï de manera erràtica i, ocasionalment, que bategui massa ràpid. Pot ser mortal."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:245
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_4b86e3cb:

    # n "Apparently, I've had it for a long time. They said it was a miracle that I was able to go on so long without anything happening."
    n "Aparentment, l'he tingut durant molt de temps. M'han dit que és un miracle que hagi pogut fer vida normal tant de temps sense que hagi passat res."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:247
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ad0a9930:

    # n "Is that really a miracle? I guess it was supposed to make me feel better, more appreciative of my life."
    n "De debò és un miracle? Suposo que m'havia de fer sentir millor, apreciar més la meva vida."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:249
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_98d930a8:

    # n "It really didn't do anything to cheer me up."
    n "La veritat és que no va fer res per animar-me."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:251
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_40bfb4d0:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=150}My parents, I think, were hit harder by the news than I was. They practically had two hemorrhages apiece."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=150}Crec que als meus pares la notícia els va afectar més que a mi. Pràcticament van tenir dues hemorràgies cadascun."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:255
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_faed1ade:

    # n "{vspace=30}I had already had a full day by then to digest everything. To them, it was all fresh. They were even willing to sell our house in order to pay for a cure."
    n "{vspace=30}Aleshores, jo ja havia tingut un dia sencer per digerir-ho tot. Per a ells, en canvi, era nou. Fins i tot estaven disposats a vendre la nostra casa per poder pagar una cura."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:257
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_4aa0947a:

    # n "{vspace=60}Of course there isn't a cure."
    n "{vspace=60}Per descomptat, no hi ha cura."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:259
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_9651b812:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=30}Because of the late discovery of this… condition, I've had to stay at the hospital, to recuperate from the treatments."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=30}A causa del descobriment tardà d'aquesta… malaltia, m'he hagut de quedar a l'hospital per recuperar-me dels tractaments."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:263
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_b8f7da43:

    # n "When I was first admitted, it felt as if I was missed…"
    n "Al principi d'ingressar-me, sentia que tothom em trobava a faltar…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:265
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_34e8419d:

    # n "For about a week, my room in the ward was full of flowers, balloons and cards."
    n "Durant cosa d'una setmana, la meva habitació a l'hospital va estar plena de flors, globus i targetes."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:267
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_090f9328:

    # n "But, the visitors soon dwindled and all the get-well gifts began trickling down to nothing shortly after."
    n "Però de seguida, el flux de visitants va baixar, i poc després, tots els regals i els bons desitjos es van reduir en no res."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:269
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_909d8632:

    # n "I realized that the only reason I had gotten so many cards and flowers was because sending me their sympathy had been turned into a class project."
    n "Vaig saber que l'única raó per la qual vaig rebre tantes targetes i flors era perquè enviar-me els seus bons desitjos era part d'un projecte de classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:271
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_b5c56144:

    # n "Maybe some people were genuinely concerned, but I doubt it. Even in the beginning, I barely had visitors. By the end of the first month, only my parents came by on a regular basis."
    n "Potser alguns estaven genuïnament preocupats, però ho dubto. Fins i tot al principi, amb prou feines rebia visites. Cap al final del primer mes, només els meus pares venien regularment."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:273
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_928fd142:

    # n "Iwanako was the last to stop visiting."
    n "La Iwanako va ser la darrera en deixar de visitar-me."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:275
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_625ffaf6:

    # n "After six weeks, I never saw her again. We never had that much to talk about when she visited, anyway."
    n "Passades sis setmanes, mai més no la vaig tornar a veure. De totes maneres, mai havíem tingut gaire de què parlar quan em visitava."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:277
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_22eef6f6:

    # n "We didn't touch the subject that was between us on that snowy day ever again."
    n "No vam tornar a tocar el tema que hi havia entre nosaltres aquell dia nevat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:279
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_5a39979d:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=30}The hospital?"
    new "[_n_] {vspace=30}L'hospital?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:283
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_91226342:

    # n "It's not really a place I'd like to live in."
    n "Realment no és un lloc on m'agradaria viure."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:285
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_1bf6fc5e:

    # n "The doctors and nurses feel so impersonal and faceless."
    n "Els metges i les infermeres semblen tan impersonals i buits."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:287
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ccb3302d:

    # n "I guess it's because they are in a hurry and they have a million other patients waiting for them, but it makes me feel uncomfortable."
    n "M'imagino que és perquè estan saturats i tenen un milió de pacients més esperant-los, però això no em fa sentir menys incòmode."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:289
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ecf33f47:

    # n "For the first month or so, I asked the head cardiologist every time I saw him for a rough estimate of when I'd be able to leave."
    n "Durant el primer mes o així, cada cop que veia al cap de cardiologia li demanava una estimació aproximada de quan podria marxar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:291
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_baa2d8b8:

    # n "He never answered anything in a straightforward way, but told me to wait and see if the treatment and surgeries worked."
    n "Mai em va respondre de forma directa, sinó que em deia que havíem d'esperar i veure si el tractament i les intervencions quirúrgiques funcionaven."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:293
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ab6e12e7:

    # n "{vspace=30}So, I idly observed the scar that those surgeries had left on my chest slowly change its appearance over time, thinking of it as some kind of an omen."
    n "{vspace=30}Així que observava absentment com la cicatriu que aquelles intervencions m'havien deixat al pit canviava d'aspecte lentament amb el temps, pensant que era una mena d'auguri."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:295
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_4a32222f:

    # n "I still ask the head cardiologist about leaving, but my expectations are low enough now that I'm not disappointed any more when I don't get a reply. The way he shuffles around the answer shows that there is at least some hope."
    n "Encara li pregunto al cardiòleg quan podré marxar, però les meves expectatives ja són prou baixes per no desil·lusionar-me quan no rebo una resposta. La forma amb la qual dona voltes a la resposta demostra que almenys hi ha alguna esperança."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:297
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_e0fa902a:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=120}At some point I stopped watching TV. I don't know why, I just did."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=120}En algun moment, vaig deixar de veure la televisió. No sé per què; simplement, ho vaig deixar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:301
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_2a59d03b:

    # n "Maybe it was the wrong kind of escapism for my situation."
    n "Potser era una forma d'escapisme equivocada per a la meva situació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:303
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_6a2081cc:

    # n "{vspace=30}I started reading instead. There was a small 'library' at the hospital, although it was more like a storeroom for books. I began working my way through it, one small stack at a time. After consuming them, I would go back for more."
    n "{vspace=30}En comptes, vaig començar a llegir. Hi havia una petita \"biblioteca\" a l'hospital, tot i que era més aviat magatzem de llibres. Vaig començar a llegir-los de pila en pila. Quan m'acabava una pila, tornava a buscar-ne més."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:305
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_aefc9b82:

    # n "I found that I liked reading and I think I even became a bit addicted. I started feeling naked without a book in my hands."
    n "Vaig descobrir que m'agradava llegir, i crec que fins i tot m'hi vaig tornar una mica addicte. Vaig començar a sentir-me despullat sense un llibre a les mans."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:307
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_eb6d0c5d:

    # n "{vspace=30}But I loved the stories."
    n "{vspace=30}Però les històries m'encantaven."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:309
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_b319e002:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=30}That was what my life was like."
    new "[_n_] {vspace=30}I així era la meva vida."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:313
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_3e9487ef:

    # n "{vspace=30}The days became increasingly harder to distinguish from each other, differing only by the book I was reading and the weather outside. It felt like time blurred into some kind of gooey mass I was trapped inside, instead of moving within."
    n "{vspace=30}Cada cop era més difícils distingir uns dies dels altres, i només es diferenciaven pel llibre que estava llegint o les condicions meteorològiques de fora. Era com si el temps s'hagués difuminat fins a convertir-se en una mena de massa enganxosa dins la qual estava atrapat, en comptes de moure-m'hi per dins."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:315
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_937b0b7c:

    # n "A week could go by without me really noticing it."
    n "Podia passar perfectament una setmana sencera sense que me n'adonés."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:317
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_c525cbef:

    # n "Sometimes, I'd pause in realization that I didn't know what day of the week it was."
    n "De vegades, m'aturava quan m'adonava que no sabia ni quin dia de la setmana era."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:319
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_257a2271:

    # n "But other times, all the things that surrounded me would painfully crash into my consciousness, through the barrier of nonchalance I had set up for myself."
    n "Però d'altres vegades, tot allò que m'envoltava xocava dolorosament amb la meva consciència, travessava la barrera de despreocupació que havia erigit al meu voltant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:321
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_75fad3d1:

    # n "The pages of my book would start to feel sharp and burning hot and the heaviness in my chest would become so hard to bear that I had to put the book aside and just lay down for a while, looking at the ceiling as if I was going to cry."
    n "Les pàgines del llibre de torn començaven a ser afilades i ardents, i l'opressió del pit se'm tornava tan difícil de suportar que havia de deixar el llibre i simplement estirar-me una estona, mirant al sostre com si estigués a punt de posar-me a plorar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:323
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_3997609c:

    # n "But that happened only rarely."
    n "Però això passava poc sovint."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:325
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_6da0fc3c:

    # n "{vspace=30}And I couldn't even cry."
    n "{vspace=30}I ni tan sols podia plorar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:331
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_f77d5b5d:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "Today, the doctor comes in and gives me a smile. He seems excited, but not very. It's like he is trying to make an effort to be happy on my behalf."
    new "Avui, el doctor entra i em somriu. Sembla emocionat, però tampoc massa. És com si estigués intentant fer un esforç per alegrar-se per mi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:335
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_145a949c:

    # "My parents are here. It's been a few days since I've last seen them. Both of them are even sort of dressed up. Is this supposed to be some kind of special occasion? It's not a party."
    "Els meus pares estan aquí. Han passat uns dies des de l'últim cop que els vaig veure. Tots dos van més ben del que és habitual. Se suposa que aquesta és una ocasió especial? No és cap festa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:337
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_bcb11816:

    # "There is this ritual the head cardiologist has. He takes his time, sorting his papers, then setting them aside as if to make a point of the pointlessness of what he just did."
    "El cap de cardiologia té una espècie de ritual. Es pren el seu temps per repassar els seus papers, i llavors els aparta com si volgués deixar clar que això que acaba de fer no té sentit."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:339
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_645ccc5e:

    # "Then he casually sits down on the edge of the bed next to mine. He looks me in the eyes for a moment."
    "Aleshores, s'asseu despreocupadament a la vora del costat del llit. Em mira un moment als ulls."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:341
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ae1dc4a1:

    # "Doctor" "Hello, Hisao. How are you today?"
    "Doctor" "Hola, Hisao. Com estàs avui?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:343
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_74264518:

    # "I don't answer him but I smile a little, back at him."
    "No responc, però somric una mica, de retorn al seu."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:345
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_a9872b53:

    # "Doctor" "I believe that you can go home; your heart is stronger now, and with some precautions, you should be fine."
    "Doctor" "Crec que te'n pots anar a casa; el teu cor ja és més fort, i amb algunes mesures preventives, tot hauria d'anar bé."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:347
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_84464266:

    # "Doctor" "We have all your medication sorted out. I'll give your father the prescription."
    "Doctor" "Tenim tota la teva medicació decidida. Li donaré la recepta al teu pare."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:349
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_d20e71ba:

    # "The doctor hands a sheet of paper to my dad, whose expression turns wooden as he reads it quickly."
    "El doctor li passa un full de paper al pare, que posa cara de circumstàncies mentre el llegeix per sobre."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:351
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_b9806ad0:

    # "Dad" "So many…"
    "Dad" "Quin munt…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:353
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_36ab31f4:

    # "I take it from his hand and take a look myself, feeling numb. How am I supposed to react to this?"
    "Li agafo el paper de les mans i li faig una ullada, quedo atordit Com se suposa que he de reaccionar a això?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:364
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_049cd67b:

    # "The absurdly long list of medications staring back at me from the paper seems insurmountable. They all blend together in a sea of letters."
    "La llista absurdament llarga de medicaments que em torna el paper sembla insalvable. Tots alhora es mesclen en un oceà de lletres."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:366
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_a91ebedb:

    # "This is insane."
    "Això és de bojos."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:368
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_e1582878:

    # "Side effects, adverse effects, contraindications and dosages are listed line after line with cold precision."
    "Els efectes secundaris, els efectes adversos, les contraindicacions i les dosis apareixen llistades línia rere línia amb una precisió freda."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:370
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_43634d79:

    # "I try to read them, but it's so futile."
    "Intento llegir-les, però és inútil."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:372
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_dd4cb7e0:

    # "I can't understand any of it. Attempting to only makes me feel sicker."
    "No entenc res del que hi ha aquí escrit. I intentar-ho només em fa sentir pitjor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:374
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_a87d8486:

    # "All this… for the rest of my life, every day?"
    "Tot això… cada dia de la resta de la meva vida?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:383
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_fbb2c13a:

    # "Doctor" "I'm afraid that is the best we can do at this point."
    "Doctor" "Per desgràcia, això és el millor que podem fer arribats a aquest punt."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:385
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ce45deb5:

    # "Doctor" "However, new medications are always being developed, so I wouldn't be surprised to see that list fade over the years."
    "Doctor" "No obstant això, sempre s'estan desenvolupant nous medicaments, així que no em sorprendria pas que aquesta llista disminuís amb el pas dels anys."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:387
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_dc324ee1:

    # "Years… What kind of confidence booster is that? I'd have felt better if he hadn't said anything at all…"
    "Anys… Quina mena de confiança creu que m'insufla així? Hauria estat molt millor que no hagués dit res en absolut…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:389
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_8a2def8e:

    # "Doctor" "Also, I've spoken with your parents and we believe that it would be best if you don't return to your old school."
    "Doctor" "A més, he parlat amb els teus pares, i creiem que seria millor que no tornessis al teu antic institut."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:391
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_269d3433:

    # "What!?"
    "Què?!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:393
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_8b741e48:

    # "Dad" "Please, calm down, Hisao. Listen to what the doctor has to say…"
    "Dad" "Si us plau, calma't, Hisao. Escolta això que diu el doctor…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:395
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_10489774:

    # "Calm down? The way he says it tells me he knew full well that I wouldn't like it. Am I going to be home schooled?"
    "Que em calmi? La manera com m'ho diu em deixa prou clar que sabia perfectament que no m'agradaria la idea. Que potser m'educaran a casa?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:397
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_e5f6e2c7:

    # "Whatever of my concern shows, it's ignored."
    "Sigui quina sigui la meva preocupació, la ignoren."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:399
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_81b432ed:

    # "Doctor" "We all understand that your education is paramount; however, I don't think that it's wise for you to be without supervision."
    "Doctor" "Entenem perfectament que la teva educació és essencial; tot i això, no crec que sigui encertat deixar-te sense cap mena de supervisió."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:401
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_39aaa66d:

    # "Doctor" "At least not until we're sure that your medication is suitable."
    "Doctor" "Almenys, no fins que estiguem completament segurs que la medicació és l'adequada."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:403
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_6aa50d84:

    # "Doctor" "So, I've spoken to your parents about a transfer."
    "Doctor" "Per tant, he proposat als teus pares un traspàs."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:405
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_e8fc164c:

    # "Doctor" "It's a school called Yamaku Academy that specializes in dealing with disabled students."
    "Doctor" "És una escola anomenada Yamaku Academy, que s'especialitza a tractar alumnes amb discapacitats."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:407
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_df01d864:

    # "Disabled? What? Am I…"
    "Discapacitats? Què? Soc…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:409
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_e721b086:

    # "Doctor" "It has a 24-hour nursing staff and it's only a few minutes from a highly regarded general hospital. The majority of students live on the campus."
    "Doctor" "Té personal d'infermeria actiu les 24 hores del dia i està a pocs minuts d'un hospital general de gran prestigi. La majoria dels estudiants viuen en el campus."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:411
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_a7b43cb3:

    # "Doctor" "Think of it as a boarding school of sorts. It's designed to give students a degree of independence, while keeping help nearby."
    "Doctor" "Pensa-hi com una mena d'internat. Està dissenyat per donar als estudiants un cert grau d'independència, alhora que tenen ajuda a prop."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:413
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_a64d3c87:

    # "Independence? It's a school for disabled kids. Don't try to disguise that fact."
    "Independència? És una escola per a nens discapacitats, per l'amor de Déu. No intentis disfressar-ho."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:415
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_edda9b03:

    # "If it was really that 'free,' there wouldn't be a 24-hour nursing staff, and you wouldn't make a hospital being nearby a selling point."
    "Si de veritat fos tan \"lliure\", no hi hauria personal d'infermeria les 24 hores del dia, i tampoc no en faries de la proximitat a un hospital un argument per vendre-m'ho."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:417
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_dde7915e:

    # "Dad" "Of course, that's only if you want to go. But… your mother and I aren't really able to home school you."
    "Pare" "Per descomptat, això és només si hi vols anar. Però… la teva mare i jo realment no podem educar-te a casa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:419
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ec5265c6:

    # "Dad" "We went out there and had a look a couple of weeks back; I think you'd like it."
    "Pare" "Vam anar-hi a fer un cop d'ull fa un parell de setmanes; crec que t'agradaria."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:421
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_3a7cc194:

    # "It looks like I really don't have a choice."
    "No sembla que tingui més opció."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:423
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_a3e36ce4:

    # "Doctor" "Compared to other heart problems, people with your condition usually tend to live long lives. You'll need a job one day and this is a good opportunity to continue your education."
    "Doctor" "Comparat amb altres problemes de cor, la gent amb la teva malaltia sol viure una vida llarga. Necessitaràs feina algun dia, i aquesta és una bona oportunitat per continuar la teva educació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:425
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_e54aea15:

    # "This isn't an opportunity, don't call it an opportunity. Don't call it a goddamned opportunity."
    "Això no és cap oportunitat, no n'hi diguis oportunitat. No n'hi diguis puta oportunitat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:427
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_61bc19a8:

    # "Doctor" "Well, you should be excited at the chance to go back to school. I remember you wanted to return to school, and while it's not the same one…"
    "Doctor" "Bé, hauries d'estar emocionat per l'oportunitat de tornar a l'institut. Recordo que volies tornar-hi i, tot i que no és el mateix…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:429
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_51d6fade:

    # "A special school. That's…"
    "Una escola especial. Això és…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:431
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_96f69568:

    # "An insult. That is what I want to say. It's a step down."
    "Un insult. Això és el que vull dir. És un pas enrere."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:433
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_c39dab3f:

    # "Dad" "It's not what you think. All of the students there are pretty active, in their own sort of way."
    "Pare" "No és el que creus. Tots els estudiants que hi ha són força actius, cadascú a la seva manera."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:435
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_5b0cb836:

    # "Dad" "It's geared towards students that can still get around and learn, but just need a little help… in one way or another."
    "Pare" "És un lloc dissenyat perquè els estudiants puguin valer-se per si mateixos i aprendre, però amb una mica d'ajuda… d'una manera o altra."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:437
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_3176a865:

    # "Doctor" "Your father's right. And many of the graduates of the school have gone on to do amazing things. A person doesn't have to be held back by their disability."
    "Doctor" "El teu pare té raó. I molts dels que s'hi han graduat han fet coses sorprenents. Una persona no té perquè veure's frenada per la seva discapacitat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:439
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_4ea4b688:

    # "Doctor" "One of my colleagues in another hospital is a graduate."
    "Doctor" "Un dels meus col·legues, que treballa a un altre hospital, es va graduar en aquesta escola."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:441
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_344dd572:

    # "I don't care. A person doesn't have to be held back by their disability? That's what a disability is."
    "No m'importa. Que una persona no ha de veure's frenada per la seva discapacitat? D'això es tracta tenir una discapacitat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:443
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_900fe4f3:

    # "I really hate that something so important was decided for me. But what can I do about it? A 'normal' life is out of the question now."
    "Odio de veritat que hagin decidit per mi una cosa tan important. Però, què hi puc fer? Una vida \"normal\" ja està fora del meu abast."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:447
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_85fe91c3:

    # "It's funny, I had always thought my life was actually kind of boring, but now I miss it."
    "És curiós, de fet sempre havia pensat que la meva vida era força avorrida. Ara la trobo a faltar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:449
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_183a60a8:

    # "I want to protest. I want to blame this lack of reaction on shock, or fatigue. I could easily yell out something now - something about how I can go back to school anyway. But, no."
    "Vull protestar. Vull culpar aquesta manca de reacció al xoc o a la fatiga. Ara no em faria res cridar - alguna cosa sobre com puc tornar ara a l'escola, de totes maneres. Però no."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:451
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_ef15775a:

    # "I don't say anything. The fact is that I know now it's futile."
    "No dic res. El fet és que ara sé que això no serviria de res."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:453
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_43220101:

    # "I look around the room, feeling very tired of all this. The hospital, doctors, my condition, everything. I don't see anything that would make me feel any different."
    "Miro al voltant de l'habitació, i em sento molt cansat de tot això. L'hospital, els metges, el meu estat, tot. No veig res que em pogués fer sentir diferent."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:455
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_86af7b40:

    # "There really isn't a choice. I know this, but the thought of going to a disabled school… what are those even like? As much as I try to put a positive spin on this, it's very difficult."
    "Realment no tinc elecció. Ho sé, però la idea d'anar a una escola per a discapacitats… com són aquesta mena de llocs? Per molt que intenti mirar-ho des del cantó positiu, és molt difícil."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:457
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_1aa4ad31:

    # "But let me try."
    "Però deixa'm intentar-ho."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:459
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_37181d88:

    # "A clean slate isn't a bad thing."
    "No és dolent començar de cap i de nou."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:461
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_9de30fc4:

    # "That is all I can think of to get me through this. At least I still have something; even if it's a 'special school,' it's something. It's a fresh start, and my life isn't over. It would be a mistake to just resign myself to thinking that."
    "Això és l'únic que se m'acut per sortir-me'n d'aquesta. Almenys encara tinc alguna cosa; tot i que sigui una \"escola especial\", segueix sent millor que res. És un nou començament, i la meva vida no ha acabat. Seria un error resignar-me a pensar això."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:463
translate ca a1_monday_bundle_of_hisao_213354d2:

    # "At the very least, I'll try to see what my new life will look like."
    "Com a mínim, provaré de veure com serà la meva nova vida."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:476
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_8cc5b1b8:

    # "The gate looked far too pompous for what it was."
    "La reixa d'entrada semblava massa pomposa pel que era."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:478
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_91a39e93:

    # "In fact, gates in general seem to do that, but this one especially so."
    "De fet, les reixes en general semblen ser-ho, però noi, aquesta s'emporta la palma."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:480
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_b831d73a:

    # "Red bricks, black wrought iron and gray plaster, assembled into a whole that didn't feel welcoming at all."
    "Rajols vermells, ferro negre forjat i guix d'un to grisós, combinats junts no semblava gens acollidor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:482
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_8c69e9ba:

    # "I wondered if it looked like what a gate for a school should look like, but couldn't really decide. Probably no."
    "Em preguntava si aquest realment és l'aspecte que hauria de tenir la porta principal d'una escola, però no ho tenia clar. Probablement no."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:484
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_77bd59f8:

    # "Of course I didn't want to get stuck on thinking about the gate for too long, so I entered through it with a brisk pace that felt surprisingly good."
    "Per descomptat, no volia quedar-me massa estona pensant en l'entrada, així que la he creuat a pas lleuger i m'he sentit sorprenentment bé."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:486
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_590f903f:

    # "Moving forward feels good."
    "Moure's endavant és una bona sensació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:491
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_682e1471:

    # "So I walk towards the main building of Yamaku Academy with this brisk pace. I'm alone, as my parents are taking my stuff to the dorms, and there's supposed to be someone waiting for me."
    "Així, camino amb aquest pas lleuger cap a l'edifici principal de l'Acadèmia Yamaku. Estic sol, ja que els meus pares m'estan portant les coses al dormitori, i se suposa que hi ha algú que m'espera."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:493
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_e15f3543:

    # "The grounds are incredibly lush, filled with green."
    "Els voltants són increïblement frondosos, plens de verd."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:495
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_96a709dc:

    # "It doesn't feel like the kind of grounds a school would have, more like a park, with a clean walkway going past trees and the smell of fresh-cut grass and all other park-like things."
    "No sembla la mena d'entorn que normalment tindria una escola, sinó que més aviat d'un parc, amb un caminet que passa entre els arbres i l'olor de gespa acabada de tallar, i totes les altres coses que esperaries veure en un parc."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:497
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_a2aa6b19:

    # "Words like 'clean' and 'hygienic' pop into my mind. It makes me shudder."
    "Em venen al cap paraules com ara \"net\" i \"higiènic\". I em venen esgarrifances."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:499
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_1f324b32:

    # "I shake them off. Stay open-minded now. It's your new life. You have to take it as it comes."
    "Me les trec de sobre. Has de ser obert de ment, ara. És la teva nova vida. Les coses s'han d'acceptar tal com venen."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:501
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_160489d9:

    # "That's what I tell myself."
    "Això és el que em dic a mi mateix."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:503
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_184e52e4:

    # "A few big buildings loom behind the leafy canopies, too big and too many for just a school."
    "Darrere les frondoses capçades dels arbres, apareixen uns grans edificis, són massa grans i n'hi ha masses per ser només una escola."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:505
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_fb309d6a:

    # "Everything seems off; it's different from what I thought I knew about schools."
    "Tot sembla fora de lloc; és diferent de tot allò que creia que sabia sobre les escoles."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:507
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_f9bee95e:

    # "It's an uncanny valley. Even though I was told this is my new school, in the back of my head it doesn't feel like one."
    "És una vall inquietant. Em van assegurar que aquest era el meu nou institut, però en el fons no ho sento pas així."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:509
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_8da4006e:

    # "I wonder if the feeling is real or caused by my expectations of a school for the disabled."
    "Em pregunto si el sentiment és real o bé causat per les meves expectatives sobre com seria una escola per a discapacitats."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:511
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_68907d46:

    # "Speaking of that, I don't see anyone else here. It's kinda eerie."
    "Parlant d'això, no veig a ningú més per aquí. És una mica estrany."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:513
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_9d24677d:

    # "It makes me wish there was somebody here so I could anchor myself to something tangible instead of having this feeling that I stepped into another dimension."
    "Si hi hagués algú, almenys podria aferrar-me a alguna cosa tangible, en comptes de tenir aquesta sensació inquietant d'haver entrat en una altra dimensió."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:515
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_06c766f8:

    # "The trees hum with the wind and the green hues flashing all around me catch my attention."
    "Els arbres murmuren amb el vent i els tons de verd que brillen al meu voltant em capten l'atenció."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:517
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_2174bda6:

    # "It makes me think about hospitals again, how they say that the operating rooms are painted green because green is a calming color."
    "Em fa pensar un altre cop en els hospitals, en això que diuen que pinten els quiròfans de color verd perquè és un color que ajuda a calmar-se."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:519
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_238b28c7:

    # "So why am I feeling so anxious, despite all this greenery?"
    "Si és així, per què estic tan neguitós enmig de tanta verdor?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:521
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:523
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_73020a48:

    # "Only after I stand in front of the haughty main building, I surprise myself by realizing why the gate bothered me:"
    "Només quan em planto davant el superb edifici principal, em sorprenc a mi mateix en adonar-me de per què la porta d'entrada a l'institut m'incomodava tant:"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:525
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_58949436:

    # "It was the last chance I had to turn back, even if I had no life I could return to."
    "Era l'última oportunitat que tenia de tornar enrere, encara que no tingués cap vida a la qual pogués tornar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:527
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_663574d2:

    # "But still, after entering, there was absolutely no way I could go back any more."
    "Però, tot i això, després d'entrar, ja no tenia possibilitat de fer marxa enrere."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:529
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_91f59619:

    # "Feeling nervous and with this realization set in my head, I open the front door."
    "Nerviós i amb aquesta certesa al cap, obro la porta principal de l'edifici."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:534
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_02dc57b4:

    # "A tall man with bad posture notices me as I enter. We're the only people in the lobby, so it's only logical."
    "Un home alt amb mala postura es fixa en mi només entrar. Som les úniques persones que hi ha al vestíbul, així que és lògic."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:539
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_efa1be84:

    # mu_ "You must be… Ni… Na… Niki?"
    mu_ "Tu deus ser en… Ni… Na… Niki?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:541
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_379f1eff:

    # hi "Nakai."
    hi "Nakai."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:546
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_7d56ca54:

    # mu_ "So you are. Excellent. I'm your homeroom and science teacher. My name is Mutou."
    mu_ "Sí, ho ets. Excel·lent. Jo soc el teu tutor i professor de ciències. Em dic Mutou."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:548
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_266ecf56:

    # mu "Welcome."
    mu "Benvingut."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:550
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_903ab41f:

    # "We exchange a handshake that is neither firm nor sloppy, and he looks at his watch."
    "Fem una encaixada de mans que no és ni massa forta ni massa fluixa, i aleshores es mira el rellotge."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:555
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_7585988e:

    # mu "The head nurse asked you for a brief check-in visit, but there's no time for that now."
    mu "L'infermer en cap volia fer-te una breu visita de control, però ara ja no tenim temps per fer-la."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:557
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_c3708bb8:

    # hi "Oh. Should I go later?"
    hi "Oh. Hi vaig després, doncs?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:562
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_ef817f31:

    # mu "Yes, afternoon is probably fine. We should get going and introduce you to the rest of the class. They're waiting already."
    mu "Sí, a la tarda segurament serà un bon moment. Hauríem d'anar tirant i presentar-te a la resta de la classe. Ja t'estan esperant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:564
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_a6a89f26:

    # "Waiting for me? I don't really like being the center of attention, but I guess it's inevitable in a situation like this."
    "M'esperen a mi? No és que m'agradi gaire ser el centre d'atenció, però suposo que és inevitable en aquesta situació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:566
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_71c3fa98:

    # "Somehow, not knowing what is waiting for me makes me feel really nervous."
    "D'alguna manera, no saber què és el que m'espera em posa molt nerviós."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:568
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_5f509620:

    # "Thinking of this, I almost miss what the teacher is saying."
    "Pensant-hi, gairebé em perdo això que el professor m'està dient."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:574
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_e0337dc3:

    # mu "Do you want to introduce yourself to the class?" nointeract
    mu "Vols presentar-te tu mateix a la classe?" nointeract

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:590
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_65b25d93:

    # "My heart is pounding in my chest and it keeps me thinking about my condition as I follow the teacher up the stairs."
    "El cor em va a mil i no puc deixar de pensar en la meva malaltia mentre segueixo el professor escales amunt."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:596
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_3a81219e:

    # "The third door down the third floor corridor is marked as the classroom for class 3-3."
    "La tercera porta del passadís de la tercera planta està identificada com l'aula per la classe 3-3."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:600
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_b4cd4d35:

    # "Mutou opens the door and enters."
    "En Mutou l'obre i entra."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:609
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_7e77e825:

    # mu "Good morning everyone, sorry I'm late again."
    mu "Bon dia a tothom, perdoneu que torni a arribar tard."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:613
translate ca a1_monday_gateway_effect_7b458bd2:

    # "I hesitate for a split second at the door, freezing on the spot."
    "Em quedo uns segons indecís davant la porta, paralitzat per la situació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:621
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_e74e2c41:

    # "Ah, get a grip! This is a big step, I know that… But there isn't any point to worrying so much about it, at least not this soon."
    "Au, calma't! És un gran pas, ho sé… però no té sentit que me'n preocupi tant, almenys no tan aviat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:628
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_1f0fc33a:

    # "I follow the teacher into the classroom and look around, partially so I won't have to meet the curious gazes of my new classmates."
    "Segueixo el professor a dins de l'aula i miro al meu voltant, en part, per tal de no trobar-me amb les mirades curioses dels meus nous companys."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:630
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_7fc32931:

    # "It's pretty spacious; the ceiling is unusually high and there's lots of space left over around and inbetween the desks."
    "És una aula prou àmplia; el sostre és inusualment alt, i hi ha un munt d'espai lliure al voltant i entre les taules."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:632
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_c5cc5e23:

    # "An entire wall taken up by blackboards and the high, old fashioned windows only make it seem larger."
    "Una paret sencera coberta de pissarres i les finestres són tan altes i antiquades que fa que sembli encara més gran."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:634
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_83e64db2:

    # "The students' desks are just standard wooden desks with a shelf underneath for books and wooden chairs with metal frames. Simple and efficient."
    "Els pupitres dels estudiants són les típiques taules de fusta amb un calaix a sota per guardar-hi els llibres, i cadires de fusta amb potes metàl·liques. Simple i eficient."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:636
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_d86573b7:

    # "I stop walking in front of the classroom and face the other students. They all look normal, like students in any other school. But then, why would they be here?"
    "M'aturo davant la classe i miro a la resta d'estudiants. Tots semblen normals, com els alumnes de qualsevol altra escola. Llavors, què hi fan aquí?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:640
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_a9c0f533:

    # "They're probably like me and have something wrong with them, only it's just not immediately obvious. Then, I notice that one of the girls seems to be missing the thumb of her right hand. It's a little jarring."
    "De segur que són com jo i els passa alguna cosa, però que no és immediatament òbvia. Aleshores m'adono que una de les noies sembla no tenir dit polze a la mà dreta. És una mica desconcertant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:642
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_0a84f341:

    # "Despite the natural tendency to listen when someone's talking about you, I tune out the teacher's speech halfway through while he introduces me to the class."
    "Al marge de la tendència natural d'escoltar quan algú parla de tu, em desconnecto a la meitat del discurs del professor mentre em presenta a la resta de la classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:644
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_9a6ff8f5:

    # "I notice a flash of dark hair and see that someone is looking at me. A girl with really long, straight hair that is pretty eye-catching. As she sees me looking back at her, she covers her face with her hands as if it will make her invisible."
    "Noto un llampec de cabells foscos i veig que algú m'està mirant. Una noia amb els cabells molt llargs i llisos que crida força l'atenció. Quan veu que li torno la mirada, es tapa la cara amb les mans com si això la fes invisible."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:646
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_12584c35:

    # "There is one boy with a cane leaning against the lockers at the rear of the class. It's weird seeing someone so young with a cane."
    "Hi ha un noi amb un bastó recolzat als armariets del fons de la classe. És estrany veure algú tan jove portant un bastó."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:648
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_f7a8e507:

    # "Another girl seems to be making some weird hand motions. Sign language? She peers at me over the rims of her glasses, then goes back to whatever she's doing."
    "Una altra noia sembla fer moviments estranys amb les mans. Llenguatge de signes? Em mira per sobre de les ulleres i torna al que fos que estava fent."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:650
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ae488323:

    # "She's kind of cute. So is the cheery-looking girl with pink hair sitting next to her. She's really hard to miss; I don't know how I didn't notice her the moment I walked in…"
    "És força guapa. Com també ho és la noia alegre amb cabells de color rosa que té al seu costat. És realment difícil passar-la per alt; no sé pas com no m'hi he fixat quan he entrat…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:652
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_b3c5aeb3:

    # mu "…please welcome our newest classmate."
    mu "…doneu la benvinguda al vostre nou company."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:654
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_2975736e:

    # "He claps his hands and so does everyone else, except one girl in the first row who has only one hand. I cringe a little, but hide it by bowing in thanks for this applause I did not deserve."
    "Aplaudeix i tota la resta també, menys una noia de la primera fila que només té una mà. M'arronso una mica, però ho dissimulo fent una reverència per agrair aquest aplaudiment que no mereixo."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:657
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_52894b81:

    # "A collective silence tells me that I should open my mouth now."
    "Un silenci col·lectiu em diu que ara seria el moment d'obrir la boca."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:659
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_921b5957:

    # hi "So… I'm Hisao Nakai."
    hi "Bé… em dic Hisao Nakai."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:661
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_8623bd84:

    # "And after that?"
    "I després d'això?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:663
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_6e0d1b33:

    # hi "My hobbies are reading and soccer. I hope to get along well with everyone even though I'm a new student."
    hi "Les meves aficions són la lectura i el futbol. Espero poder portar-me bé amb tothom tot i ser un estudiant nou."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:665
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_8623bd84_1:

    # "And after that?"
    "I després d'això?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:667
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_4374dbdf:

    # "I'm being so boring. This is exactly like every self-introduction ever. I should say something more. Something more exciting."
    "Estic sent força avorrit. Això és exactament com qualsevol altra autopresentació. Hauria de dir alguna cosa més. Alguna cosa més emocionant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:669
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_df8e17dd:

    # "I end up saying nothing, and the teacher picks up from there."
    "Al final, acabo per no dir res més, i el professor pren de nou la paraula."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:671
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_a1ab870e:

    # "Everyone seems to be satisfied even with what little I said, though. A few girls are whispering to each other, throwing glances at me. It could've gone worse."
    "Tanmateix, tothom sembla satisfet fins i tot amb les poques coses que he dit. Algunes noies xiuxiuegen entre elles mentre m'estudien amb la mirada. Bé, podria haver anat pitjor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:673
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:675
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_6df9a126:

    # "After the applause, there is a brief silence that nobody seems to want to be responsible for breaking."
    "Després de l'aplaudiment, hi ha un breu silenci que ningú sembla voler ser responsable de trencar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:677
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_817975a1:

    # "The teacher soon realizes that he should probably say something. He opens up with some unintelligible noise, shuts up as he loses his momentum, and then starts introducing me."
    "El professor s'adona de seguida que potser hauria de dir alguna cosa. Comença amb un soroll inintel·ligible, calla quan perd l'impuls, i comença a presentar-me."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:679
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_8e841327:

    # "Nobody seems to be too interested."
    "Ningú sembla estar gaire interessat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:681
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_27b35f61:

    # "Maybe I should've said yes to the self-introduction thing."
    "Potser hauria d'haver dit que sí a això de presentar-me jo mateix."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:683
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_bdaaa0b8:

    # "Probably realizing he doesn't know anything about me, he just ends up saying my name wrong again, and asks me to write it on the blackboard."
    "Probablement s'adona que no sap res de mi, acaba dient el meu nom malament un altre cop, i em demana que l'escrigui a la pissarra."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:685
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_e95363d2:

    # "I do that, and turn back to face the class, feeling awkward."
    "Ho faig, i em torno a girar cap a la resta de la classe, amb una sensació incòmoda."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:689
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_8c3d6576:

    # "I listen to the teacher as he drones about getting along while letting my gaze sweep across the classroom."
    "Sento que el professor no para de parlar sobre la convivència, mentre passejo distretament la mirada per la classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:691
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_5dc2fa5e:

    # "Everyone seems to be listening to him intently and when he's done, they clap their hands again which feels like a weird thing to do."
    "Tothom sembla estar escoltant-lo atentament i, quan acaba, tornen a aplaudir-lo, cosa que em sembla estranya."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:693
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_74702b00:

    # "The first row girl claps on this round, with her one hand against her other wrist that ends in a bandaged stump."
    "La noia de la primera fila també aplaudeix aquest cop, amb la mà contra el canell de l'altre braç, que acaba en un monyó embenat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:695
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_2a5034be:

    # "It makes me feel a little bad."
    "Em fa sentir una mica malament."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:701
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_90b478db:

    # mu "We're going to be doing some group work today, so that'll give you a chance to talk with everyone. Is that okay with you?"
    mu "Avui treballarem en grup, o sigui que tindràs l'oportunitat de parlar amb tothom. Et sembla bé?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:703
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_9a959fb3:

    # hi "Yeah, it's fine with me."
    hi "Sí, cap problema."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:708
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_99ccb9af:

    # mu "That's good, you can work with Hakamichi. She is the class representative."
    mu "Perfecte, doncs, pots treballar amb la Hakamichi. Ella és la delegada de classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:710
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_9710e177:

    # mu "She can explain anything you might want to know. And who else would be able to do that better, right?"
    mu "Pot explicar-te tot el que vulguis saber. I qui més podria fer-ho millor, veritat?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:715
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_83656091:

    # "How could I know?"
    "Com vol que jo ho sàpiga?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:717
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_7aac71e2:

    # "The teacher passes out the day's assignments and announces that we will be working in groups of three."
    "El professor reparteix les tasques del dia i anuncia que treballarem en grups de tres."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:719
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_186f41a7:

    # "It hits me that I don't know who Hakamichi is. Slow. The teacher seems to catch my helpless expression."
    "M'adono que no tinc ni idea de qui és la Hakamichi. Que n'arribo a ser de lent. El professor sembla que capta la meva expressió de confusió."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:721
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_c02fc09c:

    # mu "Oh, right. Hakamichi is right there, Shizune Hakamichi."
    mu "Oh, cert. La Hakamichi és allà, la Shizune Hakamichi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:726
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_9780a72e:

    # "As he calls out her name, the cute, bubbly looking girl with bright pink hair and gold eyes waves her hand at me. I take a seat next to her, by the window."
    "Quan la crida pel seu nom, una noia bonica i alegre amb cabells de color rosa i ulls daurats, em saluda amb la mà. M'assec a la seva esquerra, al costat de la finestra."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:728
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_db5de56f:

    # hi "Hey, I guess you're Hakamichi, right? It's nice to meet you."
    hi "Hola, suposo que ets la Hakamichi, oi? Encantat de conèixer-te."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:735
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_f4e61544:

    # mi_shi "Hahaha~!"
    mi_shi "Hahaha~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:737
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_e5274dd8:

    # "What? I'm caught off guard by her laughter."
    "Què? La seva rialleta m'agafa totalment desprevingut."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:742
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_928e68e1:

    # mi_shi "It's nice to meet you, too!{w=0.5} But~!"
    mi_shi "És un plaer conèixer-te, també!{w=0.5} Però~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:744
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_381424fc:

    # mi_not_shi "It's nice to meet you, too! But~!{fast}, I'm not Hakamichi, I'm Misha! This is Hakamichi. Shicchan~!"
    mi_not_shi "És un plaer conèixer-te, també! Però~!{fast}, jo no soc la Hakamichi, em dic Misha! Ella és la Hakamichi. Shicchan~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:755
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_cb0e7a92:

    # "Giggling, Misha points to the girl next to her, the one I saw using sign language before. It looks like she has been staring at me this whole time. She nods once nonchalantly to show that she acknowledges my presence… but only barely."
    "Tot rient, la Misha assenyala la noia del seu costat, la que abans he vist fent servir llenguatge de signes. Sembla que m'ha estat mirant tota aquesta estona. Assenteix amb indiferència per mostrar-me que aprecia la meva presència... però en prou feines."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:757
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_8a27b1c8:

    # "She has short, yet carefully, neatly brushed hair, a pair of oval-shaped glasses balanced on the tip of a dainty nose, and dark blue eyes that seem to alternate every few seconds between analytical and slightly bored."
    "Té els cabells curts, però ben pentinats, duu unes ulleres ovalades que se li equilibren a la punta delicada del nas, i els ulls de color blau fosc semblen alternar cada pocs segons una expressió analítica amb una de mig avorriment."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:759
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_17c12c85:

    # hi "It's nice to meet you."
    hi "És un plaer."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:764
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:775
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_59205ed6:

    # "She immediately looks at Misha, who smiles and makes a few quick gestures with her hands."
    "De seguida mira a la Misha, que somriu i fa uns quants gestos ràpids amb les mans."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:783
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_1a20b6b5:

    # "Hakamichi nods and makes a few gestures of her own."
    "La Hakamichi fa que sí amb el cap i respon amb uns gestos."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:785
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_67f82955:

    # "I start to wonder if the teacher was messing with me, saying things like 'you'll be able to talk to people' and 'who better to explain things to you.'"
    "Començo a preguntar-me si el professor m'estava prenent el pèl, dient-me coses com \"podràs parlar amb els altres\" i \"qui millor per explicar-te les coses\"."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:790
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_5977d9d2:

    # mi "I can see you're a little confused, right?, right? But, I understand why you would think I was Shicchan!"
    mi "Veig que estàs una mica confós, oi? Oi? Però entenc per què t'has pensat que jo era la Shicchan!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:792
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_133025c7:

    # mi "Shicchan is deaf, so I'm the person who translates things back and forth for her."
    mi "La Shicchan és sorda, i jo soc la persona que tradueix el que diu als altres i a l'inrevés."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:797
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_d40e5af3:

    # mi "I'm like an interpreter~! She says it's nice to meet you, too!"
    mi "Soc com una intèrpret~! També diu que és un plaer conèixer-te!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:802
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:807
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_5d25e220:

    # mi "You're the new student, aren't you? Well, Shicchan, of course he is! If he wasn't, he would have been standing up there for no reason, right? Right~!"
    mi "Tu ets l'estudiant nou, oi? Bé, Shicchan, és clar que ho és! Si no ho fos, s'hauria passat tota aquesta estona dempeus allà al davant per no res, oi? I tant~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:810
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_6d373ce7:

    # mi "He seems like a very interesting person, doesn't he~!"
    mi "Sembla una persona força interessant, oi que sí~?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:812
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_5055dece:

    # "Misha looks at me with a weird expression, then continues."
    "La Misha em mira amb una expressió estranya, i continua parlant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:814
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_eeb7ddd2:

    # mi "We don't know much about him, but maybe we'll find out later."
    mi "No en sabem gairebé res, però potser després esbrinarem més coses."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:816
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_77427e26:

    # "Maybe I should've introduced myself after all. Anything would've given a better first impression than the teacher's drone and fumbling with my name."
    "Ben mirat, potser sí que m'hauria d'haver presentat jo mateix. Qualsevol cosa hauria donat més bona primera impressió que la xerrameca del professor i les seves patinades intentant pronunciar bé el meu nom."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:818
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_10f39980:

    # mi "We knew there was going to be a new student, but we didn't know you would be here today. So soon! Hicchan, right?"
    mi "Sabíem que vindria un nou estudiant, però no que seria avui mateix. Que aviat! Hicchan, oi?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:820
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_6ee129ea:

    # "Hicchan…?"
    "Hicchan…?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:825
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_cb832926:

    # mi "Yup~! It fits, doesn't it?"
    mi "Sí~! T'escau força, veritat?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:827
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_d84fbefe:

    # "Did I say it out loud? It's just a surprise. I've never liked that nickname."
    "Que potser ho he dit en veu alta? Quina sorpresa. Mai no m'ha agradat aquest sobrenom."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:829
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_5d7883ed:

    # hi "I don't really see how."
    hi "No veig pas com m'hauria d'escaure."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:834
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_2281c7be:

    # mi "It fits~! You look just like I imagined!"
    mi "T'escau~! Ets exactament com m'imaginava!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:839
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:845
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_63c361c9:

    # mi "Hahahaha~! Yeah, you look just like a Hicchan!"
    mi "Hahahaha~! Sí, en fas cara de Hicchan!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:847
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ac579bec:

    # hi "I wonder why everyone seems to think so…"
    hi "Em pregunto per què tothom pensa així…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:849
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:851
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_567db65a:

    # "Hakamichi taps her fingers on the desk to get Misha's attention. They gesture back and forth to each other excitedly, their hands a blur."
    "La Hakamichi colpeja suaument els dits sobre la taula per cridar l'atenció de la Misha. Gesticulen entre elles animadament, amb les mans gairebé difuminades."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:865
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_b88c3c2d:

    # "Misha seems a little overwhelmed."
    "La Misha sembla una mica aclaparada."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:870
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_69144008:

    # mi "Ahaha~! Er, sorry about that!"
    mi "Ahaha~! Eh, perdona!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:875
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_b54ebb0a:

    # mi "Shicchan wants you to know that she's the class rep, so if there is anything you need to know, you can feel free to ask her."
    mi "La Shicchan vol que sàpigues que és la delegada de classe, així que si hi ha qualsevol cosa que necessitis saber, no dubtis a preguntar-l'hi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:880
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:885
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_cdde91a5:

    # mi "Do you like the school so far? We can show you around a little if you haven't had the time to walk around and…{w=0.5}{nw}"
    mi "T'agrada el que has vist de l'escola fins ara? Podríem ensenyar-te-la una mica si no has tingut temps de passejar-te i…{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:890
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ee780a73:

    # extend " familiarize?{w=0.5}{nw}"
    extend "familiaritzar-te?{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:895
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_f3c21d86:

    # extend " yourself with it!"
    extend "familiaritzar-t'hi!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:897
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_27c5fbb2:

    # "Misha stumbles with the hard word a bit, making it stick out in her otherwise fluid translation."
    "La Misha s'entrebanca una mica amb aquesta expressió complexa, fent que es desviï de la seva traducció, per la resta força fluida."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:899
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_9621c045:

    # hi "Thanks, that would be pretty helpful. Yeah, I just kind of came straight to class today."
    hi "Gràcies, això m'ajudaria força. Sí, avui he vingut gairebé de dret a classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:904
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_5:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:909
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_66b999fb:

    # mi "Hahaha~!"
    mi "Hahaha~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:914
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_06b6506c:

    # mi "That's no good! You should always try to learn as much as you can about where you're going before you go there. Not just with school, either~!"
    mi "Això no està bé! Sempre hauries d'intentar aprendre tant com puguis del lloc on aniràs abans d'anar-hi. I no només de l'escola, qualsevol lloc~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:919
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_2855793f:

    # mi "Always! Even if it's a trip to the convenience store! Really, Shicchan? Hahaha~!"
    mi "Sempre! Fins i tot si és una sortida al supermercat! De debò, Shicchan? Hahaha~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:925
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_0c8e9144:

    # "Learn about where you're going? I guess I didn't bother to do that, or just didn't care enough to do so."
    "Informar-te del lloc on aniràs? Suposo que no em vaig preocupar a fer-ho, o simplement no m'importava prou per fer-ho."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:927
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_32458251:

    # "I didn't look forward to this, even if I committed myself to go along with it half-assedly, but anyway."
    "No en tenia gaires ganes, tot i que em vaig comprometre a acceptar-ho a mitges, però en fi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:929
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_72f4de8f:

    # "I don't say anything, and Misha signs something that ends in a shrug. What was that? It seems like it was about me."
    "No dic res, i la Misha gesticula alguna cosa que acaba en un encongiment d'espatlles. Què era això? Sembla que es referia a mi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:931
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_db473724:

    # "I feel like slumping over in my seat. Both of them are smiling, but that shrug hit me unexpectedly deeply."
    "Em venen ganes de desplomar-me sobre la cadira. Totes dues somriuen, però aquest encongiment d'espatlles m'afecta molt més que no em pensava."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:936
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_005b757f:

    # mi "You look down, are you okay?"
    mi "Sembles abatut, estàs bé?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:941
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_6:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:946
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_aaf4c0a4:

    # mi "Don't take it the wrong way, please~! I hate it when people are afraid to ask questions! That's how people learn things, by asking~!"
    mi "No t'ho prenguis malament, si us plau~! Odio quan la gent té por de fer preguntes! Així és com s'aprenen les coses, preguntant~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:948
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_a4029863:

    # mi "Asking for help is perfectly normal, as much as needing help! Stop looking like you just failed a test!"
    mi "Demanar ajuda és tan normal com necessitar-la! Deixa de fer cara d'haver suspès un examen!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:953
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_69277904:

    # mi "Wahahaha~!"
    mi "Pffhahaha~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:955
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_4b6419d2:

    # hi "All right."
    hi "Com vulguis."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:960
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_7:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:965
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_5439cec0:

    # mi "Ah, and another thing, you don't have to call Shicchan something so formal like 'Hakamichi' or 'class rep' all the time! Just call her Shicchan~!"
    mi "Ah, i una altra cosa, no has de cridar a la Shicchan amb noms formals com \"Hakamichi\" o \"delegada\" tota l'estona! Ja va bé si li dius Shicchan~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:972
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_8:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:977
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_0918f486:

    # mi "Ahaha~! Okay, maybe that's too casual. Maybe 'Shizune' would be more appropriate?"
    mi "Ahaha~! D'acord, potser m'he passat d'informal. Potser \"Shizune\" seria més apropiat?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:982
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_9:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:989
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_4893f27e:

    # mi "Yup, yup~! 'Shizune' is fine!"
    mi "Sí, sí~! \"Shizune\" va bé!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:991
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_54ccbe97:

    # hi "Heh. Okay, that would be a lot easier for me."
    hi "Heh. Entesos, també serà molt més fàcil per mi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:993
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_3338243c:

    # "I feel a lot more at ease. Both of them seem so friendly, so I feel like an idiot for being so apprehensive earlier. Especially about Shizune, who I assumed would be all business."
    "Em sento molt més a gust. Totes dues semblen força amables, així que em sento com un idiota per haver estat tan aprensiu. Especialment pel que fa a la Shizune, que assumia que seria molt seriosa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:995
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_b7e9a02d:

    # "Well, she still seems like that. Just less so, I guess."
    "Bé, de fet encara m'ho sembla. Una mica menys, suposo."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1000
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "...!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1005
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_95424f1c:

    # mi "Huh? Oh, right, we haven't even touched the assignment! We should start work now, or Shicchan will get mad."
    mi "Eh? Oh, és veritat, encara no hem tocat la feina! Hauríem de començar a treballar ja, o la Shicchan s'empiparà."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1007
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_7bd0067e:

    # hi "The assignment is also kind of long, so we should start now if we want to finish it before the end of class."
    hi "També sembla força llarg, o sigui que hauríem de començar ara si volem acabar-la abans del final de la classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1012
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_542a2800:

    # mi "Wahaha~! That too!"
    mi "Pffhaha~! Això també!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1017
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_10:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1019
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_15488b74:

    # "Shizune glares at the two of us impatiently. I don't need to know sign language to understand that."
    "La Shizune ens mira a tots dos amb impaciència. No necessito saber llenguatge de signes per entendre-ho."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1021
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_b04afdfa:

    # hi "Okay, okay, I get the message."
    hi "D'acord, d'acord, ja capto el missatge."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1026
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_ef2b123c_11:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1031
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_2e692fb8:

    # mi "After class, we can take a walk around the grounds together. It's a nice day today! Okay~?"
    mi "Després de classe, podem donar una volta junts pel campus. Avui fa bon dia! Què us sembla~?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1033
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_f4fbe215:

    # "The assignment is actually very challenging to get through, combining aspects of being both difficult and unnecessarily long."
    "La tasca és realment molt difícil, ja que combina aspectes de dificultat i duració innecessària alhora."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1040
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_d5ae6efe:

    # "Still, we finish it a few minutes earlier than anyone else in the class, despite our late start. Shizune and Misha are really capable."
    "Tot i això, l'acabem uns minuts abans que la resta de la classe, fins i tot comptant que hem començat tard. La Shizune i la Misha són realment competents."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1042
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_6fecd237:

    # "They're quite different, though. The class rep is as calm and professional as she looks, while Misha is a lot more playful and girlish. Not to mention a little more easily distracted."
    "Tanmateix, són força diferents. La delegada és tan calmada i professional com aparenta, mentre que la Misha és molt més juganera i femenina. No cal dir que també es distreu amb molta més facilitat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1044
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_8885c900:

    # "To be honest, the two of them did most of the work. I feel guilty about that."
    "Per ser franc, entre les dues han fet gran part de la feina. I això em fa sentir culpable."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1048
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_14bb5b19:

    # "The clock tower bells ring, signaling the end of the period. Time for lunch."
    "Sonen les campanes del rellotge de la torre, assenyalen el final de la classe. És hora de dinar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1053
translate ca a1_monday_enter_stage_left_2a1f6d53:

    # "Without knowing what else to do, I follow Misha, who is beckoning me into the hallway and down the stairs."
    "Sense saber què més fer, segueixo la Misha, que em fa senyals perquè la segueixi pel passadís i baixi escales avall."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1062
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_8ea3432e:

    # "We descend even below the lobby where I met Mutou, down to the bottom floor."
    "Baixem més per enllà del vestíbul on m'he trobat abans amb en Mutou, cap al pis inferior."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1069
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_1bffb9a8:

    # "Just like everything in this school, the cafeteria seems too spacious and oddly modern in contrast to the classic exterior."
    "Com tot a aquesta escola, la cafeteria sembla massa espaiosa i estranyament moderna, en contrast amb l'exterior clàssic."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1071
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_2747dc72:

    # "Its big windows open to the courtyard, towards the main gate."
    "Els grans finestrals s'obren al pati, cap a la porta principal."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1078
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_b6f3f127:

    # mi "It's the cafeteria~!"
    mi "Això és la cafeteria~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1080
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_1a2cf4d9:

    # "Her enthusiastic statement of the obvious makes people around us stare, but Misha doesn't seem to care so we proceed to the line."
    "El seu comentari entusiàstic d'això tan obvi atreu les mirades de la gent que ens envolta, però a la Misha no sembla pas importar-li així que ens col·loquem a la fila."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1085
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_39e02dea:

    # "There is a rather long list of menu options, which seems great until I realize that many of them are to accommodate students who need special diets."
    "Hi ha una llista força llarga d'opcions al menú, que sembla genial fins que m'adono que moltes són pels estudiants que necessiten dietes especials."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1087
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_af4a00e4:

    # "How nice. It almost feels like I'm back at the hospital, eating portions measured with scientific precision to meet the needs of the patients."
    "Que bé. Em sento com si hagués tornat a l'hospital, menjant porcions calculades amb precisió científica per tal d'ajustar-se a les necessitats dels pacients."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1089
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_0c514f1e:

    # "I pick something at random and follow Shizune to a table, sitting opposite of her."
    "Agafo una opció a l'atzar, i segueixo a la Shizune fins a una taula, m'assec de cara a ella."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1095
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_6cbd33d7:

    # "As I nibble indifferently at the food I'd rather not eat, Misha pokes me in the side to get my attention and points to Shizune."
    "Mentre rosego amb indiferència el menjar que gairebé preferiria ni tastar, la Misha em clava un dit a les costelles per cridar-me l'atenció i assenyala a la Shizune."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1101
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1103
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_7639786c:

    # "I don't understand sign, so the point escapes me."
    "No entenc els signes, o sigui que la finalitat d'això se m'escapa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1105
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_bf364854:

    # "Maybe looking at a person who 'talks' to you is proper and polite?"
    "Potser mirar a la persona que et \"parla\" és correcte i educat?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1111
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_fdbb07a1:

    # mi "Do you want to know something?"
    mi "Vols saber alguna cosa?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1113
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_81d99227:

    # hi "What?"
    hi "Què?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1118
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_00e4fdb5:

    # mi "About anything! We're your guides so you should ask if there is something~!"
    mi "El que vulguis! Som les teves guies, per tant, pregunta'ns allò que vulguis saber~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1124
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_740dd966:

    # hi "Hmm, I wonder…" nointeract
    hi "Hmm, doncs no ho sé…" nointeract

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1138
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_0e7b1408:

    # "Misha and Shizune sign back and forth very animatedly, throwing sideway glances at me but Misha refrains from translating."
    "La Misha i la Shizune intercanvien signes de forma molt animada, tot llençant-me mirades de reüll, però la Misha no tradueix res."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1140
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_fbab405d:

    # "Maybe they are talking about secret girl stuff or something."
    "Potser parlen de secrets entre noies o alguna cosa semblant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1142
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1148
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_b4f99232:

    # "I quickly notice a conversation in sign is not enough to fill a silence."
    "Ben aviat m'adono que una conversa amb llenguatge de signes no és suficient per emplenar un silenci."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1155
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_d27954d1:

    # "We arrive in the classroom early, but we're not the first."
    "Arribem d'hora a classe, però no som els primers."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1161
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a1176af9:

    # "That dark haired girl I noticed before is slumped over her desk at the last row."
    "Aquella noia de cabells foscos que he vist abans està tirada sobre el seu pupitre a l'última fila."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1169
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_7adf23da:

    # "She jumps a little when Misha crashes into the room with the elegance of a rhino."
    "Fa un bot quan la Misha irromp a l'aula amb l'elegància d'un rinoceront."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1171
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_aae42560:

    # "She shrinks deeper into her seat. I can feel her tension all the way from here, as if she were slowly turning into stone just from our presence."
    "S'encongeix més al seu seient. Puc notar la seva tensió des d'on soc, com si es convertís lentament en pedra només per la nostra presència."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1173
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_3eedcb9c:

    # "Misha and Shizune either don't notice or don't mind it, as they walk directly past her to their seats and begin to converse."
    "La Misha i la Shizune o bé no ho noten o no els importa, ja que li passen just per davant per arribar als seus seients i comencen a parlar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1180
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a6f6d656:

    # "I'm left wondering about her, even when the classroom slowly fills with other students and finally, the teacher."
    "Em quedo pensant en aquesta noia, fins i tot quan la classe es va emplenant a poc a poc amb més estudiants i, finalment, el professor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1182
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_c7cf87c9:

    # "Getting into the rhythm of school feels strange; it's as if my brain remembers how this is done, but my body doesn't."
    "Se'm fa estrany acostumar-me al ritme de l'escola; és com si el meu cervell recordés com es fa, però no el meu cos."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1184
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_1e2a25a5:

    # "Towards the end of the class I start yawning and counting the minutes left."
    "Cap al final de la classe, començo a badallar i a comptar els minuts que queden."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1186
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a764f623:

    # "I shouldn't be this tired on my first day of school."
    "No hauria d'estar així de cansat el primer dia d'institut."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1188
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_21342f19:

    # "Maybe it's the long time spent in the hospital that made me like this. I'm even feeling physically weak and lifeless."
    "Potser estar tant de temps a l'hospital m'ha fet acabar així. Fins i tot em sento físicament dèbil i sense esma."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1195
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_0ae32363:

    # "Before long, the final bell rings."
    "Al cap de no gaire, sona l'última campana."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1197
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_c368b2a5:

    # "School is finally over for the day."
    "Per fi s'ha acabat l'escola per avui."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1199
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_02edef34:

    # "Beside me, Misha and Shizune are having a short conversation. After a bit of deliberation, Misha turns to me."
    "Al meu costat, la Misha i la Shizune tenen una breu conversa. Després d'una mica de deliberació, la Misha es gira cap a mi."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1205
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1207
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_e8cd8fda:

    # mi "Unfortunately we can't stay and show you around today, Hicchan. We've got to hurry already, since there is a lot of work for us to do."
    mi "Per desgràcia avui no podem quedar-nos amb tu i guiar-te per l'institut, Hicchan. Ens hem d'afanyar, perquè tenim un munt de feina a fer."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1212
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1214
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_3829d84d:

    # mi "You'll find your way around here, I'm sure of it."
    mi "Sabràs orientar-te sol per aquí, n'estic segura."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1216
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ac26a6c3:

    # hi "Ah, wait! The teacher said I'd have to see the nurse. Where do I have to go?"
    hi "Ah, espereu! El professor m'ha dit que havia d'anar a veure a l'infermer. On he d'anar?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1222
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_35d234b9:

    # mi "Is that so? We can at least show you that much~!"
    mi "Només això? El mínim que podem fer és acompanyar-t'hi~!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1224
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef906d06:

    # mi "Come on, the nurses have their own building, so we have to go outside."
    mi "Anem, la infermeria té el seu propi edifici, o sigui que hem de sortir a fora."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1233
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_1ef45060:

    # "We join the flow of students making their way down the stairwell and outside, with the girls pointing out other senior classrooms in the same hallway as ours."
    "Ens unim a la riuada d'estudiants que s'obren camí per les escales i cap a l'exterior, mentre les noies altres classes superiors en el mateix passadís que la nostra."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1238
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_74eec774:

    # "When we get outside, the girls make their way to the smaller building right next to the school."
    "Quan arribem a fora, les noies es dirigeixen a l'edifici més petit que està just al costat de l'escola."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1240
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_f2fec5a5:

    # "It's built in the same style, so it looks like it's actually a part of the main building."
    "Està construït amb el mateix estil, així que sembla que realment és part de l'edifici principal."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1246
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1248
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ed3fd110:

    # mi "This is the auxiliary building here. There's a lot of official and important stuff inside, like the Yamaku Foundation office and all the nurses' offices. They even have a swimming pool!"
    mi "Aquest d'aquí és l'edifici auxiliar. Hi ha un munt de coses oficials i importants aquí dins, com l'oficina de la Fundació Yamaku i tots els despatxos d'infermeria. Fins i tot tenen una piscina!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1250
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_4c193a23:

    # hi "How is that official?"
    hi "Com pot ser oficial?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1255
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1260
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a22f7b7b:

    # mi "Don't be silly, Hicchan! It's for physical therapy of course."
    mi "No siguis ximple, Hicchan! És per a teràpia física, és clar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1265
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_d286341c:

    # mi "Anyway, all the nursing staff facilities are in there too. The head nurse's office is on the first floor."
    mi "Sigui com sigui, totes les instal·lacions d'infermeria també són allà dins. El despatx del cap d'infermeria és al primer pis."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1271
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_58989557:

    # mi "You'll be fine from here, right~? We'll be going, then! See you tomorrow!"
    mi "Sabràs anar-hi sol a partir d'aquí, oi~? Nosaltres marxem, doncs! Ja ens veurem demà!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1273
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ba0ffa6c:

    # hi "Yeah, thanks. Bye."
    hi "Sí, gràcies. Adeu."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1281
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_dc8917f1:

    # "A whole building for stuff that has nothing to do with the actual education?"
    "Un edifici sencer per a coses que no tenen res a veure amb l'educació en si?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1283
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_900825df:

    # "I guess it's necessary for a place like this."
    "Suposo que és necessari en un lloc com aquest."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1288
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_d0aa6077:

    # "I walk in, hoping that this really will be only a quick visit like the teacher said."
    "Entro a l'edifici, esperant que aquesta sigui una visita ràpida, tal com m'ha dit el professor."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1290
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_057ab20a:

    # "On a white door on the left is a green cross with the text 'Head Nurse' and a nameplate."
    "Sobre una porta blanca a l'esquerra, hi ha una creu verda amb el text \"Cap d'Infermeria\" i un rètol amb el nom."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1294
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_dd35dbc8:

    # "A voice from the inside responds to my knock almost immediately, but I can't quite make it out."
    "Des de dins, una veu respon gairebé de forma immediata quan truco, tot i que no entenc gaire el que acaba de dir."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1296
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_edbfd164:

    # "It sounded a bit like an invitation to open the door, so I invite myself further in."
    "Diria que ha sonat com si em convidés a obrir la porta, o sigui que entro cap a dins."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1303
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ed46b3e9:

    # "The room is not large and it smells strange. A friendly-looking man turns around on his office chair to face me as I enter."
    "L'habitació no és gran i fa una olor estranya. Un home d'aspecte amigable es gira sobre la seva cadira de despatx per mirar-me mentre entro."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1305
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_3c4908fc:

    # "His desk is neat and tidy, but the bin under the table is overflowing with used medical utensils and there are at least a dozen coffee-cup rings lingering on the desk."
    "Té l'escriptori net i ordenat, però la paperera que hi ha a sota està plena d'estris mèdics utilitzats, i hi ha almenys una dotzena de marques de vasos de cafè sobre la taula."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1312
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_73f97cb3:

    # nk_ "Hello there. What can I do for you today?"
    nk_ "Hola, nano. Què puc fer per tu avui?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1314
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_5171ebfc:

    # "He is young-looking and sort of rugged, but the dimples in his cheeks wash that impression away when he smiles."
    "Se'l veu jove i fins i tot robust, però els clotets que se li fan a les galtes quan somriu es carreguen aquest rastre."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1316
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a11df3bc:

    # hi "Erm, are you the nurse?"
    hi "Eh, és vostè l'infermer?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1321
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_61adbf9e:

    # "He smiles like a person who has heard this very same question hundreds of times."
    "Somriu com algú que ha sentit aquesta mateixa pregunta centenars de vegades."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1323
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_75ca14e6:

    # nk_ "Why yes, I am. It says so on the door, no?"
    nk_ "Doncs sí, soc jo. Ho posa a la porta, oi?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1325
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_d9931667:

    # nk_ "You can call me by my name or just 'the nurse' like everyone else."
    nk_ "Pots dir-me pel meu nom o només \"infermer\", com fa tothom."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1327
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_045b0ede:

    # "Of course. I shake off my confusion, realizing I probably should grab his extended hand.{w} His handshake is rather firm and friendly."
    "És clar. Em trec la confusió de sobre, i m'adono que potser hauria d'estrènyer-li la mà que m'ofereix.{w} La seva salutació és força ferma i cordial."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1329
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_f2b2aaa7:

    # hi "Right… err, I'm a new student and my homeroom teacher told me to come and meet you. My name is Hisao Nakai."
    hi "Entesos… eh, soc l'estudiant nou i el meu tutor m'ha dit que passés a veure'l. Em dic Hisao Nakai."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1333
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_c87430cb:

    # "His eyes light up with revelation and he snaps his fingers."
    "De sobte, els ulls se li il·luminen com si tingués una revelació mentre pica els dits."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1338
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_dd7398fb:

    # nk "Oh you're THAT Nakai. I was just reading your file in the morning."
    nk "Ah, tu ets AQUELL Nakai. Aquest matí m'he llegit el teu historial."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1340
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a0ba7d95:

    # nk "Some kind of chronic arrhythmia and related congenital heart muscle deficiency, right?"
    nk "Alguna mena d'arítmia crònica i una deficiència muscul·lar cardíaca congènita, oi?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1342
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_e2b76466:

    # "He gestures me to sit down in a vacant armchair in front of his desk."
    "Em convida amb un gest a seure a la cadira que hi ha davant del seu escriptori."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1344
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ffe3688d:

    # hi "Eh, yes."
    hi "Eh, sí."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1349
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_456bb3a5:

    # nk "Good. Well, you've probably been briefed about the school enough, so I'll just go over this quickly."
    nk "Molt bé. Vejam, ja et deuen haver informat sobre el funcionament d'aquesta escola, així que t'ho resumiré ràpidament."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1351
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_eeb9f76f:

    # nk "We have all kinds of facilities available, mostly physical therapy and such."
    nk "Tenim tota mena d'instal·lacions disponibles, la majoria per a teràpia física i coses així."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1353
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ce5292f6:

    # nk "There's always someone from my staff around, even at night, so never hesitate to call us if there is a problem."
    nk "Sempre hi ha algú del meu equip de guàrdia, fins i tot de nit, o sigui que no dubtis mai a cridar-nos si hi ha algún problema."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1355
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_394221d1:

    # "The famous twenty-four-hour nursing staff."
    "El famós servei 24 hores del personal d'infermeria."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1357
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_b2f75876:

    # hi "Wow, this is like a hospital."
    hi "Carai, això és com un hospital."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1359
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_5c66f970:

    # nk "Well, not exactly. For instance, we don't do brain surgery here."
    nk "Bé, no exactament. Per exemple, aquí no fem cirurgies de cervell."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1361
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_1132741f:

    # "His joke feels so out of place that I'm left thinking why he even said it."
    "La seva broma sembla tan fora de lloc que em quedo pensant per què ho havia de dir."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1363
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_c5af973d:

    # hi "Yeah… just that it's really weird to have so many medical people at a school."
    hi "Sí… és només que se'm fa estrany tenir tant de personal mèdic en una escola."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1365
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ef9a8929:

    # nk "You'll get used to it."
    nk "Ja t'hi acostumaràs."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1367
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_bc4e53ff:

    # "I'm not so sure of that myself but I don't let the nurse know it."
    "No n'estic pas tan segur, però no deixo que l'infermer ho sàpiga."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1369
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_8d8e9455:

    # nk "Now, let me just find your file again…"
    nk "Ara, a veure si trobo un altre cop el teu expedient…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1371
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_f1b735f6:

    # "While he searches for something from his computer and shuffles stacks of papers around, I let my gaze wander around the room."
    "Mentre busca alguna cosa al seu ordinador i regira munts de paper, aprofito per passejar la mirada al voltant de l'habitació."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1373
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_04fe514c:

    # "It's the epitome of generic, I'd like to say."
    "Gairebé es podria dir que és l'arquetip de genèrica."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1375
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_aecf46fc:

    # "Beige walls and ceiling, dark gray laminate flooring, and all the equipment you'd expect from a school nurse's office."
    "Les parets i el sostre de color beix, el terra laminat de color gris fosc i tots els aparells que esperaries veure a la infermeria d'un institut normal."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1377
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_f5b97905:

    # "Even the ridiculous educational posters are hanging on all four walls, reminding me to eat properly - three times a day and from all the food groups."
    "Fins i tot els ridículs pòsters educacionals que pengen de les quatre parets, que em recorden que mengi adequadament: tres cops al dia i de tots els grups d'aliments."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1382
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_2c148e3b:

    # "Smiling, the nurse draws a thick file from a stack of similarly thick files and opens it."
    "Somrient, l'infermer treu un expedient gruixut d'entre un munt d'expedients igual de grossos, i l'obre."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1384
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_4ca2f528:

    # nk "So, you already have medication for the arrhythmia, just remember to take your pills every morning and evening or it won't be much help."
    nk "Així doncs, ja tens medicació per l'arrítmia, només recorda prendre't totes les pastilles cada matí i cada vespre o no t'ajudaran gaire."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1389
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_35003cfa:

    # nk "Apart from that… do you do any sports? Rash stuff like… I don't know, boxing?"
    nk "A part d'això… practiques alguna mena d'esport? Coses violentes com… no sé, boxa?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1391
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_e9561c2f:

    # "He grins to his own joke but I don't."
    "L'infermer somriu a la seva pròpia broma, però jo no."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1393
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_f5df716b:

    # hi "Eh, well. I played soccer occasionally with some classmates."
    hi "Eh, bé. De vegades, jugava a futbol amb alguns companys de classe."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1395
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_184521b6:

    # nk "All right, I'm afraid I'm going to have to recommend you refrain from doing that. At least, for the time being."
    nk "D'acord, desafortunadament t'hauré de recomanar que t'estiguis de fer-ne. Com a mínim, de moment."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1397
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_04be15a3:

    # hi "Oh."
    hi "Oh."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1399
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_9c0a33a3:

    # "My lack of reaction makes him raise an eyebrow, but really, I'm not too bothered by him forbidding me to kick a ball around."
    "La meva falta de reacció li fa aixecar una cella, però realment no em preocupa gaire que m'hagi prohibit donar puntades de peu a una pilota."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1401
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ce06e48e:

    # "I guess I never did it out of burning passion for the sport. Just to have something to do."
    "Suposo que mai ho vaig fer per pura passió per aquest esport ni res semblant. Només per fer alguna cosa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1403
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_726a527d:

    # nk "Any kind of concussion might be very dangerous to your heart, and risking another attack is not a good idea."
    nk "Qualsevol commoció cerebral podria ser molt perillosa per al teu cor, i arriscar-te a patir un altre atac no és bona idea."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1405
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_c5dc59d6:

    # nk "Was the previous one caused by a sudden concussion to the chest area? There is no mention of the cause in your papers."
    nk "L'anterior va ser causat per una commoció sobtada a l'àrea del pit o alguna cosa semblant? No es menciona la causa en el teu historial."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1407
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_1c6f80c5:

    # hi "Err… not exactly."
    hi "Eh… no exactament."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1412
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_61f1a2db:

    # "I sidestep the question acceptably, and he glances at me over his papers, with a more serious expression on his face."
    "Sembla que he esquivat prou bé la pregunta, tot i que em mira per sobre dels seus papers, amb una expressió més seriosa a la cara."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1414
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_a355e6b0:

    # nk "Still, you need to keep your body healthy so some exercise would do you good."
    nk "Sigui com sigui, necessites mantenir el cos en forma, així que una mica d'exercici t'aniria bé."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1416
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_4d897c5f:

    # nk "We have physical therapy and such available as I said, but I don't think you really need such heavy measures."
    nk "Disposem d'instal·lacions de teràpia física i coses així, com ja he dit, tot i que no crec pas que necessitis mesures tan dràstiques."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1418
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_582e530e:

    # nk "Just get some light exercise regularly."
    nk "Simplement, fes una mica d'exercici suau amb regularitat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1420
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_0386f2ec:

    # nk "Brisk walks or even light jogging, jumping rope, that sort of thing. Swimming, maybe? There's a pool here."
    nk "Caminar ràpid o fins i tot córrer una mica, saltar a la corda, aquest tipus de coses. Natació, potser? També tenim una piscina."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1422
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_2dd006c0:

    # hi "So I was told."
    hi "Ja m'ho han dit."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1427
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_9a5f2557:

    # nk "You were? Very good."
    nk "Ah, sí? Molt bé."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1429
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_00cb857b:

    # nk "At any rate, and I'm sure you've been told this before, you just need to take care not to overexert yourself."
    nk "En tot cas, i n'estic segur que ja t'ho deuen haver dit abans, només cal que vagis amb compte de no esforçar-te massa físicament."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1431
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_613849c3:

    # "He wags his finger to emphasize the point. No need really, I've heard this a thousand times already."
    "Mou el dit per emfatitzar aquest punt. No fa falta, ja ho he sentit un miler de vegades."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1436
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_f396d58b:

    # nk "Absolutely no unnecessary risks. Take care of yourself."
    nk "Cap mena de riscos innecessaris. Cuida't."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1438
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "D'acord."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1440
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_8c55b28a:

    # "He goes over my papers one more time and sets them on the desk, obviously content."
    "L'infermer repassa els meus papers un cop més abans de tornar-los a deixar sobre l'escriptori, òbviament satisfet."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1445
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_ed4ec60a:

    # nk "Good. That's it, then. Come meet me if you ever need something."
    nk "Bé. Doncs això és tot. Vine'm a veure si necessites alguna cosa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1452
translate ca a1_monday_in_the_nursery_abdbfbd3:

    # "I'm ushered out before I even realize it. A quick visit, indeed."
    "Em convida a marxar abans no me n'adono. Una visita ràpida, sens dubte."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1463
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_09cdd0e3:

    # "I end up standing in front of the main building and the auxiliary building, although to my eyes, they still look one and the same."
    "Acabo parat davant de l'edifici principal i de l'auxiliar, encara que, per mi, segueixen semblant un i el mateix."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1465
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_ad9d58c1:

    # "It's the first real look I get at the other students, so I watch people coming out of the school, going towards the gate or the dorms."
    "És la primera vegada que veig a la resta d'estudiants, així que observo a la gent que surt de l'escola i va cap a la sortida o als dormitoris."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1467
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_28a8c832:

    # "Everyone seems to know where they are going."
    "Tothom sembla saber cap a on va."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1469
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_0c194d31:

    # "And I still keep thinking that most of them don't look too special for being students at a special school. Then again, neither do I."
    "I continuo pensant que la majoria no tenen cap mena d'aspecte especial per ser alumnes d'una escola especial. Tot i que, ben mirat, jo tampoc."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1471
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_57890c48:

    # "Does that make me one of them?{w} One of us?"
    "Això em converteix en un d'ells?{w} Un de nosaltres?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1473
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1475
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_95991ab2:

    # "I should go somewhere too, to prevent me from getting lost."
    "Jo també hauria d'anar a algun lloc, abans no em perdi per aquí."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1477
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_9b9e2e11:

    # "It's around dinnertime, but I feel tired instead of hungry."
    "És gairebé hora de sopar, però em sento més cansat que no pas famolenc."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1479
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_32d24f78:

    # "The weariness in me only grows as I trudge towards the dorms, set a little way apart from the main building complex."
    "El cansament no fa més que augmentar mentre avanço cap als dormitoris, que estan una mica apartats del complex principal d'edificis."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1484
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_618e9b24:

    # "There is a garden of sorts between the school and the dorms; shrubbery, flowers and that overbearing smell of fresh cut grass that fills the atmosphere."
    "Hi ha una mena de jardí entre l'escola i els dormitoris; arbusts, flors i l'olor penetrant a gespa acabada de tallar que emplena l'ambient."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1486
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_63680a1a:

    # "It dawns on my tired mind that the smell feels novel because I haven't been outside at all for so long."
    "La meva ment cansada s'adona que aquesta olor és nova perquè fa molt que no estic a l'aire lliure."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1491
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_8d1dc0fa:

    # "The dorm building is big and made of red brick. Like the others, it feels way too pompous for what it is, so I push forward, going inside."
    "L'edifici del dormitori és gran i està fet de rajola vermella. Com els altres, em sembla massa pompós per al que és, així que avanço i entro."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1496
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_5e649c59:

    # "It takes more time than necessary to fish out the key I was given from my pocket."
    "Tardo més temps del necessari a treure'm de la butxaca la clau que em van donar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1498
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_0e8d4d44:

    # hi "Room one-one-nine…"
    hi "Habitació u-u-nou…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1500
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_83541fe7:

    # "Despite the ornate exterior, the inside of the dorm is fairly new, functional, and boring."
    "Tot i l'ornamentat exterior, l'interior del dormitori és força nou, funcional, i avorrit."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1502
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_8607f636:

    # "Just like in the main building, the halls and doors are wide to accommodate wheelchairs. The same goes for the elevators at the ends of the hallways."
    "Igual que a l'edifici principal, els passadissos i les portes són prou amples perquè hi passin cadires de rodes. El mateix passa amb els ascensors al final dels passadissos."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1504
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_0b9957f4:

    # "I poke my head around the corner of the common room door."
    "Trec el cap per la cantonada de la porta de la sala comuna."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1506
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_f957e33f:

    # "Inside a few students are watching the television."
    "A dins hi ha alguns estudiants que miren la televisió."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1508
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_df8b8668:

    # "One nods and gives a quick 'hello' before turning back to the TV."
    "Un d'ells mou el cap i em dirigeix un breu \"hola\" abans de tornar a girar-se cap a la tele."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1510
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_3d87b376:

    # "Seems that only the girls around here are sociable. I suppose that's perfectly fine with me."
    "Sembla que per aquí només les noies són sociables. Suposo que no m'és pas un problema."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1512
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_941ff301:

    # "I climb the stairs to the upper floor."
    "Pujo les escales cap al pis superior."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1517
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_cbb5dc49:

    # "Here, small corridors branch off from the main hallway."
    "Aquí, petits passadissos es ramifiquen partint del passadís principal."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1519
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_fbf5c306:

    # "Each of these minor halls seems to have a toilet and shower, as well as four rooms."
    "Cadascun d'aquests passadissos inferiors sembla tenir un lavabo i una dutxa, així com quatre habitacions."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1521
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_115bd649:

    # "About halfway down the hall, I spy room 119."
    "Cap a la meitat d'aquest, hi trobo l'habitació 119."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1523
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_d85d7c63:

    # "The name plates on the rooms adjacent to mine are blank. I guess there are just two of us here."
    "Les plaques de les habitacions adjacents a la meva estan buides. Suposo que només som dos inquilins, aquí."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1528
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_a8b293a0:

    # "Light shines from below the door of room 117, so I knock lightly."
    "Una mica de llum brilla per sota la porta de l'habitació 117, així que hi truco fluixet."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1530
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_2a6ce959:

    # hi "Hello, is anyone home?"
    hi "Hola, que hi ha algú?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1532
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_f67b5981:

    # "From inside, I hear a few movements, then the clicking of way more locks than I thought these doors had. After a moment the door squeaks open."
    "Des de dins, sento uns quants moviments i després el so d'un seguit de panys i baldes que semblen més dels que pensava que tenien aquestes portes. Al cap d'un moment, la porta s'obre amb un grinyol."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1543
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_aa037744:

    # "A bespectacled boy is standing in the doorway. He is looking at me very intently through his extremely thick eyeglasses."
    "Un noi amb ulleres es planta al llindar. Em mira atentament a través de les seves lents tan gruixudes."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1545
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_24a8420d:

    # ke_ "Who is it?"
    ke_ "Qui hi ha?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1547
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_bb285c22:

    # "Blind? No, at least not completely, why would he have eyeglasses if he was?"
    "Cec? No, almenys no del tot, ja que per què hauria de portar ulleres si realment ho fos?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1552
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_71711ea9:

    # "He leans closer to me until our noses are almost touching. His breath stinks of garlic."
    "S'inclina apropant-se'm tant que els nostres nassos gairebé es toquen. L'alè li fa pudor d'alls."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1554
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_99eb9754:

    # hi "Hisao Nakai… I'm moving into the next room. I thought I should introduce my…"
    hi "Hisao Nakai... M'he traslladat a l'habitació del costat. Pensava que havia de presentar..."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1559
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_10cb9290:

    # "His face suddenly brightens in realization, and he stands back upright, thrusting his hand out in a smiling greeting, almost straight to my diaphragm."
    "De sobte, la cara se li il·lumina quan se n'adona, i es torna a posar dret mentre m'ofereix la mà tot somrient, gairebé de dret al meu diafragma."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1561
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_3ad12cb7:

    # ke_ "Oh, 'sup dude? The name's Kenji."
    ke_ "Oh, què passa, tio? Jo em dic Kenji."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1563
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_2e128558:

    # hi "Ah, hi."
    hi "Ah, ei."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1565
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_782216ab:

    # "I take Kenji's sweaty hand and shake it, still a little rattled by the sudden change of attitude and vehement welcome."
    "Agafo la mà suada d'en Kenji, li estrenyo, encara una mica desconcertat amb el canvi sobtat d'actitud i la vehement benvinguda."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1567
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_343585ee:

    # ke "There were some suspicious-looking people going in and out of your room earlier."
    ke "Hi havia un parell de persones d'aspecte sospitós entrant i sortint de la teva habitació fa una estona."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1569
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_c28424e8:

    # hi "It was probably my parents."
    hi "Devien ser els meus pares."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1574
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_baeb342e:

    # ke "Your parents? You sure? 'Cause they could've been some other people, too. You can't judge a book by its cover."
    ke "Els teus pares? N'estàs segur? Perquè podria haver estat qualsevol altre. No pots jutjar un llibre per la seva portada."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1576
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_b724408c:

    # "His out-of-place proverb is left hanging between us awkwardly as I try to think of some way to respond."
    "El seu proverbi, totalment fora de lloc, queda incòmodament penjant entre nosaltres, mentre intento pensar en alguna mena de resposta."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1578
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_0fc067d0:

    # hi "I'd say the chances are high enough."
    hi "Diria que les probabilitats eren prou altes."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1580
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_cc280403:

    # "He shudders and makes some exaggerated hand gestures."
    "El noi tremola, i fa uns quants gestos exagerats amb les mans."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1585
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_420335bb:

    # ke "You're a brave man, Hisao."
    ke "Ets un tio atrevit, Hisao."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1590
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_d6ce61c1:

    # ke "Me, I don't think I could trust the chances."
    ke "Jo no crec pas que pogués confiar en la probabilitat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1592
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_12c2656a:

    # ke "The only one I trust is myself."
    ke "L'únic en qui confio és en mi mateix."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1594
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_11180ec4:

    # hi "Does that mean I shouldn't get to know you, either?"
    hi "Això vol dir que tampoc hauria de relacionar-me amb tu, doncs?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1596
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_7c9b0b9e:

    # "He thinks about this for a while."
    "S'ho pensa un moment."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1601
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_d30479b8:

    # ke "A wise decision."
    ke "Una sàvia decisió."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1606
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_abc061c6:

    # ke "Damn, you are smarter than you look."
    ke "Collons, ets més intel·ligent del que sembles."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1608
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_7e146275:

    # ke "Probably."
    ke "Segurament."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1610
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_54d8b597:

    # ke "What do you look like? I hope not smart."
    ke "Quina pinta tens? Espero que no sigui d'intel·ligent."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1615
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_934ea0c0:

    # "He squints his eyes and leans closer again, but I lean backwards to dodge it."
    "Aleshores entretanca els ulls i torna a inclinar-se cap a mi, però aquest cop em tiro enrere per esquivar-lo."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1620
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_823da588:

    # ke "Never mind, it doesn't matter."
    ke "Tant és, no importa."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1627
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_38f22898:

    # "With that, he turns, fumbles around for a moment in search of the door handle,{w=0.3}{nw}"
    "Amb això, es gira, tempteja uns moments buscant la maneta de la porta,{w=0.3}{nw}"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1631
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_03d84824:

    # extend " and shuts the door behind him."
    extend "i tanca la porta darrere seu."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1633
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_bbe043d3:

    # "I slide the key into the lock of the door marked 119."
    "Poso la clau al pany de la porta marcada amb el número 119."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1640
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_1229ffda:

    # "Bleak beige walls, white linen, a desk made of some type of light wood. Ugly curtains."
    "Parets beix ombrívoles, llençols sobris, un escriptori fet d'alguna mena de fusta lleugera. Cortines lletges."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1642
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_d093b3f3:

    # "It's no one's room; impersonal, like my hospital room was."
    "No és l'habitació de ningú; impersonal, exactament igual que la de l'hospital."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1644
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_9bb00876:

    # "My bags are sitting at the foot of my bed, looking a lot emptier than they did this morning."
    "Les meves bosses estan als peus del llit, molt més buides del que estaven aquest matí."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1646
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_534bd6d1:

    # "The closet is sitting open, stocked with my clothes."
    "L'armari està obert, ple amb la meva roba."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1648
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_67edc698:

    # "Also, it seems that there are a number of school uniforms hanging there as well."
    "A més, sembla que també hi pengen alguns uniformes escolars."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1650
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_f35b2f64:

    # "A note is pinned to the sleeve of one of the shirts."
    "Hi ha una nota clavada a la màniga d'una de les meves camises."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1654
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_c16cf1bf:

    # "Well, at least I don't have to worry about unpacking."
    "Bé, almenys no m'he de preocupar de desfer-les."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1656
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_6fb18cff:

    # "I kind of hoped I would have, then there would be something to do."
    "Esperava que ho hagués de fer, perquè així tindria alguna cosa a fer."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1658
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_c8f2bfcd:

    # "It's still too early."
    "Encara és molt d'hora."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1660
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_7c58325a:

    # "I put the note down on the desktop and lie down on the bed, feeling drained."
    "Després de deixar la nota sobre l'escriptori, m'ajec al llit, em sento esgotat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1662
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_b6ad414a:

    # "Lying there makes me want to read something, but I have nothing with me."
    "Estar aquí estirat em fa venir ganes de llegir alguna cosa, però no he portat res."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1664
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_81db5e44:

    # "I wonder if the hospital conditioned me for wanting to read whenever I have nothing to do."
    "Em pregunto si l'hospital em va condicionar per voler llegir sempre que no tingués res a fer."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1666
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_e832e909:

    # "The restless urge just keeps growing until I have to stand up."
    "L'imperiós desig només fa que créixer, fins que m'he de tornar a aixecar."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1668
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_cc335016:

    # "Maybe it's stress or something."
    "Potser és estrès, o alguna cosa semblant."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1670
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_b06a034e:

    # "I was pretty nervous about it before coming and for the entire day today too. I still am, I think."
    "Abans d'arribar, estava força nerviós, i també durant tot el dia d'avui. De fet, crec que encara ho estic."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1672
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_6348b58a:

    # "Damn, I have to distract myself somehow, so I won't be this unnatural all the time."
    "Collons, m'he de distreure amb alguna cosa, per no ser així d'antinatural tot el temps."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1674
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_e221524e:

    # "Tomorrow, I'll go borrow some books from the library."
    "Demà, aniré a treure en préstec alguns llibres de la biblioteca."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1676
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_fd94a3a2:

    # "Yeah, I'll do that."
    "Sí, això faré."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1678
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_70c7540f:

    # "But for now…"
    "Però, ara…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1690
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_be9470dc:

    # "The bottles of medications neatly arranged on my night table catch my eye."
    "Els pots de medicaments, ordenats a la meva tauleta de nit, em criden l'atenció."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1692
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_8221a579:

    # "I pick up one and shake it just to hear the contents rattle inside, and then read the glued-on pharmacy label."
    "N'agafo un i el sacsejo, només per sentir el soroll del seu contingut, i aleshores llegeixo l'etiqueta que té enganxada."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1703
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_dcab4a88:

    # "It doesn't really say that, but it could just as well."
    "De fet, no hi posa això, però podria dir-ho perfectament."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1705
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_a55b4efc:

    # "It's kinda twisted, having your life depend on chemicals like this. I resent it a little, but what choice do I have?"
    "És una mica retorçat que la teva vida depengui d'aquesta mena de productes químics. Em molesta una mica, però, quina altra opció em queda?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1707
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_074e9993:

    # "With a sigh, I begin my new daily ritual of taking the right number of pills from each bottle, being careful to check the correct dosages."
    "Sospiro i començo el meu nou ritual diari de prendre'm el nombre correcte de pastilles de cada pot, tenint cura de comprovar les dosis correctes."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1709
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1711
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_bd65a824:

    # "I lie down again, feeling hollow and uncertain, and after that I keep staring at the blank, unfamiliar ceiling for a long time."
    "Torno a jeure, em sento buit i incert, i em quedo mirant el sostre blanc i gens familiar durant una llarga estona."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1718
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_029db9d7:

    # "It doesn't start looking any more familiar, not even after darkness falls and long shadows draw across my room like fingers."
    "No comença a semblar-me més familiar, ni tan sols quan la foscor cau per fi i llargues ombres s'estenen per la meva habitació com dits."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1720
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_a78636f5:

    # "The sheets feel slightly more comfortable, warm and nest-like against the chill that passes for room temperature here."
    "Els llençols comencen a ser una mica més còmodes, càlids i com un niu contra el fred que passa per temperatura ambient aquí."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1722
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_25eeceda:

    # "Soon the lighter shade of darkness that is the ceiling looks like every ceiling does at night, and it becomes the only thing I recognize any more."
    "Aviat, l'ombra més clara de la foscor que és el sostre s'assembla a tots els sostres de nit, i es converteix en l'única cosa que reconec."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1724
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_3031eee0:

    # "The night beckons me to sleep, and I feel the coldness of unfamiliarity and fear creeping up my spine once again."
    "La nit em convida a dormir i torno a sentir la fredor del desconeixement i el temor que em pugen per l'espina dorsal."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1726
translate ca a1_monday_nobodys_room_7220b124:

    # "I keep drifting further away from the world I knew."
    "Continuo allunyant-me del món que coneixia."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1737
translate ca a1c1o1_d1b041ee:

    # hi "Why? Do I have to?"
    hi "Per què? És obligatori?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1739
translate ca a1c1o1_c4628c14:

    # mu "Of course not. That's why I asked."
    mu "És clar que no. Per això t'ho he preguntat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1741
translate ca a1c1o1_5127e5b5:

    # hi "Right."
    hi "D'acord."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1743
translate ca a1c1o1_03b6d61b:

    # mu "Let's go then."
    mu "Som-hi doncs."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1748
translate ca a1c1o2_94d38af9:

    # hi "Yeah, sure. I mean, isn't that normal?"
    hi "Sí, és clar. Vull dir, és el normal, no?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1750
translate ca a1c1o2_f8b8190a:

    # mu "Of course. But not everyone likes to be at the center of attention."
    mu "És clar. Però no tothom se sent còmode amb la idea de ser el centre d'atenció."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1752
translate ca a1c1o2_6a185b20:

    # "I'm probably one of those people, but I guess I should be the one to give the first impression of myself."
    "Probablement, jo soc d'aquestes persones, però suposo que hauria de ser jo qui donés una primera impressió de mi mateix."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1754
translate ca a1c1o2_e57910b5:

    # hi "Right, but it's no problem."
    hi "Sí, però no passa res."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1756
translate ca a1c1o2_03b6d61b:

    # mu "Let's go then."
    mu "Som-hi doncs."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1761
translate ca a1c2o1_18fd2687:

    # hi "Oh, yeah. Is there a library in the school? Lately I've gotten into reading a lot so I'd like to check it out."
    hi "Ah, sí. Que hi ha biblioteca, a l'escola? Últimament, m'he aficionat força a llegir, i m'agradaria passar a donar-hi una ullada."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1763
translate ca a1c2o1_c4e65163:

    # "Misha gives the kind of frown that makes it clear she doesn't consider reading a healthy hobby, but then picks up her smile again."
    "La Misha fa una mena de ganyota que em deixa clar que no considera pas que la lectura sigui un hobby saludable, però aleshores recupera el seu somriure."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1765
translate ca a1c2o1_b3013764:

    # mi "There is~! It's in the second floor, we can show it to you sometime!"
    mi "Sí, n'hi ha una~! És al segon pis, t'hi podem portar en algun moment!"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1767
translate ca a1c2o1_9d5a9627:

    # hi "Thanks."
    hi "Gràcies."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1769
translate ca a1c2o1_e7bca4f8:

    # "I return to my food while the girls talk between themselves."
    "Torno a centrar-me en el meu menjar mentre les noies conversen entre elles."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1774
translate ca a1c2o2_e9a4faa1:

    # "Shizune intrigues me, and I kind of want to ask something about her."
    "La Shizune m'intriga, i tinc ganes de preguntar alguna cosa sobre ella."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1776
translate ca a1c2o2_a3cb2721:

    # "But I can't really ask about something that personal, can I?"
    "Però no puc pas preguntar una cosa tan personal, veritat?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1778
translate ca a1c2o2_08292c64:

    # "Hmm…"
    "Hmm…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1780
translate ca a1c2o2_70ea3af9:

    # "I can't come up with anything else to ask so I just focus on my food while the girls talk between themselves."
    "No se m'acut res més que m'interessi saber, així que simplement em concentro en el meu menjar mentre les noies parlen entre elles."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1785
translate ca a1c2o3_cfbb38d3:

    # hi "I can't think of anything, really."
    hi "No se m'acut res, la veritat."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1790
translate ca a1c2o3_948689c7:

    # mi "Ooh! That means we've been good guides, doesn't it, doesn't it~?"
    mi "Ooh! Això vol dir que hem sigut unes bones guies, oi que sí, oi que sí~?"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1792
translate ca a1c2o3_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1794
translate ca a1c2o3_45bdc2ce:

    # hi "Eeh… if you say so."
    hi "Eeh… si tu ho dius."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1802
translate ca a1c2o3_f71f02ad:

    # "Misha positively beams, and so does Shizune after a quick translation."
    "La Misha somriu satisfeta, i la Shizune també, després d'una ràpida traducció."

# game/script-a1-monday.rpy:1804
translate ca a1c2o3_23e15239:

    # "I shake my head at their somewhat exaggerated enthusiasm, and shift my focus on the food."
    "Espolso el cap davant el seu entusiasme una mica exagerat i em concentro de nou en el dinar."

